(9, 'Supertech Metropolis Mall, Rudrapur Saw Huge Footfall On The Eve Of Independence Day', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Metropolis Mall, Rudrapur Saw Huge Footfall On The Eve Of Independence Day</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[17&nbsp;August,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the celebration of 69th Independence Day, Supertech Metropolis Mall located in Rudrapur witnessed an enormous footfall amongst the people of the city. &nbsp;The Metropolis Mall was epitomized with the theme of tricolor especially to tune in the divine of patriotism. The d&eacute;cor of the mall had been well taken care to excite more people to be a part of three day discount offers existing at various brands in the Mall. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Metropolis Mall has associated with many mega brands such as Big Bazar, Wave Cinemas, KFC, Reliance trends, Madame, Adidas, Numero Uno, Wrangler, Levis, John Player, Pepe Jeans, Mufti , etc. One the eve of Independence Day, Big Bazaar alone had a tremendous footfall with an approximately sale of Rs 20 lakhs per day. Even the food court was observed to be running in chock-a-block, as food lovers enjoyed different delicacies at their favorite joints. It was a win-win situation for both the brand owners and customers to enjoy their shopping spree.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Metropolis Mall is a part of 50 acre Group housing development, Supertech Metropolis City and is located next to an operational 5 star hotel, Radisson Blu. Being the first time mall cum-multiplex in the entire Kumaon region, Metropolis Mall embraces every essential element of entertainment quotient such as world class indoor shopping arena, women&amp;rsquos wear, men&amp;rsquos wear, kids zone, accessories, home furnishings, multi-brand products, multi-cuisine restaurants, theaters, Wave Cinemas and the Radisson Hotel with 120 rooms . Other features of this mall are 24x7 power back up and ample parking space.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-08-17 00:00:00', 0),
(32, 'Times of India', '<p><img src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/pressCoverage/Toi%2021%20aug.jpg" /></p>\r\n', 1, 1, '2015-08-21 00:00:00', 0),
(10, 'SUPERTECH CELEBRATED INDEPENDENCE DAY ON ALL ITS PROJECT SITES', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">SUPERTECH CELEBRATED INDEPENDENCE DAY ON ALL ITS PROJECT SITES</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[15&nbsp;August,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ek Deep Shahidon Ke Naam<br />\r\nâ€‹<br />\r\nTo pay tribute to the great souls who gave their lives for Nation&#39;s independence, Supertech in â€‹association with CREDAI and Government of UP (Noida) commemorated &quot;EK DEEP SHAHIDON KE NAAM&quot; on company&#39;s 36 project sites in NCR. Supertech celebrated Independence Day Eve on August 14th, 2015 at around 7:00pm at company&#39;s respective project site by lighting diyas and candles outside the boundary of all its projects and distributing sweets to labors at the concerned project sites. This activity was successfully executed by all the key management and stakeholders of the company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>50,000 people which include contractors, skilled and unskilled laborers, employees and staff members are working on 36 projects in NCR were a part of this celebration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speaking on this occasion, Mr. R.K Arora, Chairman of Supertech Limited said &quot;Independence Day is a day of pride and glory. We are fortunate to celebrate this day with our consultants, daily wagers, employees and staff members for the cause of social welfare as we must pay tribute to the great souls who gave their lives for Nation&amp;rsquos independence. This day brings all of us together to celebrate our freedom, rejoice patriotism for our nation&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/deep-media.jpg" style="width: 650px height: 1000px" /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-08-15 00:00:00', 0),
(11, 'SUPERTECH CELEBRATES â€‹INDEPENDENCE DAY ON ALL ITS PROJECT SITES', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">SUPERTECH CELEBRATES â€‹INDEPENDENCE DAY ON ALL ITS PROJECT SITES</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[13&nbsp;August,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ek Deep Shahidon Ke Naam<br />\r\nâ€‹<br />\r\nTo pay tribute to the great souls who gave their lives for Nation&#39;s independence, Supertech in&nbsp;â€‹association CREDAIâ€‹ and Government of UP (Noida)â€‹ will commemorate &quot;EK DEEP SHAHIDON KE NAAM&quot; on its óˆ‘°â€‹ project sites. On the eve of Independence Day, Supertech will light diyas and candles outside the boundary of all its projects and distribute sweets to contractors, skilled and unskilled laborers, employees and staff membersâ€‹.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/s-banner.jpg" style="width: 700px height: 525px" /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-08-13 00:00:00', 0),
(12, 'Supertech Awarded A 500 crore Contract To Arabian Construction Company, Abu Dhabi', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Awarded A 500 crore Contract To Arabian Construction Company, Abu Dhabi</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[4&nbsp;August,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech has signed a Rs 500 crore contract with Arabian Construction Company (ACC), a renowned and experienced international Contractor from Abu Dhabi, UAE for the construction of first phase of Supertech Hues project which is a part of 70 acre Group Housing Residential development project located in Sector 68, Gurgaon.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech has awarded this contract to ACC for carrying out construction work with special construction technology, known as &amp;lsquoTunnel Form Technology&amp;rsquo. Hues will be the first project in India to be constructed with Tunnel Form Technology, which is environment friendly and delivers good quality construction. This technology is being brought for Hues in order to complete the project in 30 months. The technology will help to achieve the slab cycle of 3-4 days and to complete one tower of G+28 floors in 8 months period. &nbsp;Also it reduces dependence on large labour requirement, foreseeing the scarcity of labour in developing India. All the towers in the project will be earthquake resistant RCC Structures and all safety measures shall be used in the construction of the entire project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Architectural and Structural Designs for the towers in the project has been customized to suit the Tunnel Form Shuttering system. Specially designed Reinforcement and Concrete mixtures shall be part of construction, reducing the delivery time cycle.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talking about the contract, Mr. RK Arora, Chairman, Supertech Limited said, &amp;ldquoTo ensure possession on time, we required technology driven development and experienced contractor who can execute work as per commitment of delivery we have given to our buyers so we again signed a contract with ACC to construct our Hues project. Our association with ACC has been really long as ACC is already constructing our project Supernova in Noida. We already have trust in ACC and the kind of technologies the company uses. For the construction of Hues, ACC will be using Tunnel form technology which is very well known in other countries especially Turkey, however, Hues will be the first project in India to be constructed with this technology.&amp;rdquo&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the occasion of being awarded with one more contract with Supertech, Mr. Ani Ray, MD, ACC, said, &amp;ldquowe are thankful to Supertech for trusting us and again giving us an opportunity to construct its another project, Hues in Gurgaon, which will be constructed with the Tunnel Form technology.&amp;rdquo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Ray further added, &amp;ldquoACC salutes Supertech&amp;rsquos vision to be the Marg Darshak to achieve committed speedy delivery for its Hues customers where entire industry is struck with delivery delays. We are already constructing Spira Tower on Supertech&#39;s Supernova project with Jump Form technology, which when completed will be tallest mixed use development of India. And to get a repeat order from Supertech it reinforces the relationship to higher scale. In fact ACC and Supertech works as partners to a common cause to get the deliverables on a win -win basis rather than prevalent client-contractor relationship in the industry&amp;rdquo.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-08-04 00:00:00', 0),
(31, 'Times of India', '<p><img src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/pressCoverage/edegrsgrsgrgregregregregrge4543543543.jpg" /></p>\r\n', 1, 1, '2015-08-22 00:00:00', 0),
(13, 'Supertech Delivers Studio Apartments at River Crest, Rudrapur', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Delivers Studio Apartments at River Crest, Rudrapur</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[28&nbsp;July,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With gaiety and enthusiasm, Supertech celebrated possession ceremony of Studio Apartments at its grand township &amp;ldquoRiver Crest&amp;rdquo in Rudrapur, Udham Singh Nagar after having handed over its prestigious Mega Township &amp;ldquoMetropolis City&amp;rdquo where about 1500 families have already checked in. The Company announced possession of 112 units of loaded studio apartments having furniture, air-conditioner, LED TV &amp; Fridge and other appliances, kitchenette, cupboard etc. as part of 25 Acre integrated development. The salient features of this development include a modern Gymnasium, Swimming Pool, Indoor Games facility, Community Centre, Play Area/Park etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Studio Apartments are a part of first phase of development of the &amp;ldquoRiver Crest&amp;rdquo Project. The ceremony was attended by key officials of the Company and nearby 300 buyers of apartments alongwith their families. The gala event comprised of lavish food accompanied by mesmerizing music to be remembered for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spread in an area of 25 acres, River Crest offers plots, villas and an ultra exclusive neighborhood to the elite residents of this luxury township. Locational advantage of proximity to industrial and commercial centres, connectivity to major towns and cities, distance of only 8 KMs from Airport and 5 KMs from Railway Station, located on the main NH-87, pollution-free environment, pleasant weather, all make this project attractive to all those who look for comfortable riverside living surrounded by scenic beauty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shri R K Arora, Chairman, Supertech Limited, said on the occasion &quot;I am delighted to hold the celebration marking possession of first phase of this integrated development, to the valued buyers of Supertech River Crest Project. It is indeed a moment for celebration as we are delivering what we promised to our customers.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ideally located in the SIDCUL area of Rudrapur on the National Highway-87, River Crest has best amenities including 24x7 power back-up, round the clock security, centralized control room for the entire security management, electronic surveillance through CCTV cameras, a fully dedicated play area for kids and a club to enjoy best of the living among others. It also provides great connectivity to the key destinations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/inthenew-rcr-pic1.jpg" style="width: 650px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/inthenew-rcr-pic2.jpg" style="width: 650px" /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-07-28 00:00:00', 0),
(14, 'Mr. R.K. Arora, Chairman, Supertech Limted with Mr. Unmukt Chand, Former India Under-19 cricket team in Supertech office in NOIDA.', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Mr. R.K. Arora, Chairman, Supertech Limted with Mr. Unmukt Chand, Former India Under-19 cricket team in Supertech office in NOIDA.</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[23&nbsp;July,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/ikjuunyhbbgyjhjh.jpg" style="width: 600px height: 450px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/ssdddsdsdssdsdsdxrtrttr.jpg" style="width: 600px height: 450px" /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-07-23 00:00:00', 0),
(15, 'Supertech has come up with a ''2% Scheme''', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech has come up with a &#39;2% Scheme&#39;</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[30&nbsp;May,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech has come up with a&nbsp; &#39; 2% Scheme&#39; wherein the customer has to pay just 2% at the time of booking an apartment and rest 8%, in next six months and balance 10% will be due at the offer of possession . The 2% scheme comes with additional subvention scheme where in 80% of the total consideration will be financed by participating lender, EMI of which will borne by the customer starting offer of possession or 36 Months (24 or 12 Months in certain projects) whichever is earlier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This scheme is applicable on company&#39;s projects such as Eco Village and Sports Village in Greater Noida West, Azalia and Hill Town in Gurgaon and Golf Village at Yamuna Expressway and company&#39;s other projects in NCR</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-03-30 00:00:00', 0),
(17, 'Creche Services for Children Of Labourers', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Creche Services for Children Of Labourers</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[1&nbsp;May,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech Foundation - Supertech&#39;s CSR Trust has started the creche services at &quot;Creche&quot; at its Eco Village -3 project site. Under this initiative, children of laborers working at the project sites will be provided primary education which is very essential for any child. This initiative will also take care of kids heath and well being. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On Labor Day, May 1, around 100 children were invited at the class rooms being structured by the developer. Around 5 teachers were present to attend the children who took their first class that day and also gave away biscuits and juices to the kids.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The &quot;Creche&quot; services will be extended to other project sites as well.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/csrcresch1.jpg" style="width: 500px height: 333px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/csrcresch2.jpg" style="width: 500px height: 333px" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-05-01 00:00:00', 0),
(20, 'Supertech''s Director Shares Knowledge at - International Seminar on Development of Township', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech&#39;s Director Shares Knowledge at - International Seminar on Development of Township</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[21&nbsp;April,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UP Housing &amp; Development Board on completion of its 50 years of existence organized an &quot;International Seminar on Development of Township&quot; on 3rd April 2015 at Lucknow. The agenda for the conference was &quot;Green and Sustainable Living&quot;. The seminar saw the participation of key personnels from various industries such as construction, real estate, ancillary and related educational institutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the seminar, to deliver a lecture on &quot;Affordable Housing using Precast Technology&quot; under the session &#39;Affordability Vs Sustainability&#39; category, Mr. Anil Kumar Seth, Director, Supertech Precast Technologies Pvt. Ltd was invited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Alok Ranjan, Housing Commissioner, UP Housing Board was the Chief Guest at the seminar.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-04-21 00:00:00', 0),
(21, 'Supertech Announced Hill Town At Sohna Road, Gurgaon', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Announced Hill Town At Sohna Road, Gurgaon</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[15&nbsp;April,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech Limited has announced a premium township project, Hill Town at Sector 2, Sohna Road, Gurgaon. The company is investing Rs. 1,000 crores in this township project and Rs. 4,000 crores in all its projects in Gurgaon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hill Town is an integrated township of 140 acres which offers 2 and 3 bedroom 3 side open premium residences christened as Hill View Residences, lavish villas and independent floors. &nbsp;The township also has spaces for retail and commercial activities, school, hospital, community centre, taxi stand, beauty parlour, ATM, kids&amp;rsquo play area and a 15000 sq. ft. of clubhouse which has a Mini Theater, Gymnasium, Badminton court, tennis &amp; squash courts, Yoga and meditation pavilions, Library and party halls. Located on the foothills of the Aravallis, Hill Town will render a stellar view of the hills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speaking on the launch of Hill town, Mr. R K Arora, Chairman, Supertech Limited said &amp;ldquoHill Town is our third project in the Millennium City and as we have received an overwhelming response from our past two projects, we expect the same from this township project as well. The kind of demand we have observed in this market has encouraged us to come with a premium living project in the lap of nature. By adding Hill Town project in our company&amp;rsquos portfolio, the toal area of development is approximately 400 acres and investment is Rs. 4,000 crores in Haryana region&amp;rdquo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hill Town also has Golf Putting greens, Rock Climbing, Jogging Tracks, Cricket Pitches, Elders&amp;rsquo Garden, Organic Farming and beautifully landscaped gardens.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&amp;ldquoHill Town is an integrated township which will be delivered in phases, 1st phase is expected to be deliverd in 3 years of time and the entire project by December 2020. We are putting in an amount of Rs. 1,000 crore to develop this township&amp;rdquo, said Mr. Mohit Arora, Managing Director, Supertech Limited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the foothills of Aravallis, Hill Town is strategically located in close proximity to educational and medical centres like KR Mangalam University, GD Goenka School, Medanta Medicity, 20 minutes drive from major commercial hubs in Sector 48 &amp; 49, Gurgaon and is 25 minutes away from Cyber City Park.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/htpc1.jpg" style="width: 600px height: 375px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/htpc2.jpg" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/htpc3.jpg" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/htpc4.jpg" /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2015-04-15 00:00:00', 0),
(22, 'Supertech Limited Organized Bhoomi Pujan Of Hill Town, Sohna Road', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited Organized Bhoomi Pujan Of Hill Town, Sohna Road</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[29&nbsp;March,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech Limited, India&#39;s leading real estate developer, developer conducted the Bhoomi Pujan of a premium township project, Hill Town at Sector 2, Sohna Road, Gurgaon. The ceremony marked the commencement of construction of the township.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hill Town is an integrated township which offers premium residences, villas, independent floors, retail and commercial spaces, school, hospital, community centre, clubhouse, etc. Located on the foothills of the Aravallis, Hill Town will render a stellar view of the hills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The bhoomi pujan ceremony was performed by Mr. RK Arora, Chairman, Mrs. Sangeeta Arora, Joint Managing Director, Mr. Mohit Arora, Managing Director and other key officials of the company in the presence of around 700 customers. The ceremony was followed by scrumptious lunch and a detailed tour of the beautiful site of Hill Town, which is set in the lap of nature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the foothills of Aravallis, Hill Town is strategically located in close proximity to educational and medical centres like KR Mangalam University, GD Goenka School, Medanta Medicity, 20 minutes drive from major commercial hubs in Sector 48 &amp; 49, Gurgaon and is 25 minutes away from Cyber City Park.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="720">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="right">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/htbp1.jpg" /></td>\r\n			<td align="right"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/htbp2.JPG" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="right">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		