(23, 'Supertech Announced The Opening of Metropolis Mall in Rudrapur', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Announced The Opening of Metropolis Mall in Rudrapur</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[23&nbsp;March,&nbsp;2015]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech has announced the opening of Metropolis Mall in Rudrapur - the only mall-cum-multiplex of Kumaon region. Brands like Big Bazaar have already started rolling in making it the first retail outlet of Big Bazaar of Kumaon region.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located on National Highway-87, the Metropolis Mall is a one stop destination for a world class indoor shopping arena and multi-cuisine restaurants. The mega brands that are associated with the mall are Wave Cinemas, KFC, Reliance trends, Madame, Adidas, Numero Uno, Wrangler, Levis, John Player, Pepe Jeans, Mufti, etc and they will be opening shortly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speaking on the opening, Mr. R. K. Arora, Chairman of Supertech Limited said, &quot;We are happy to bring the first mall of Kumaon region, the Metropolis Mall in Rudrapur. We have tied-up with very good brands in every field that will cater to the demands of people living in the vicinity. Some of the brands have already started moving in amongst which Big Bazaar is the recent one. This is the very first outlet of Big Bazaar in Kumaon region&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="720">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="right">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/mpbb1.jpg" /></td>\r\n			<td align="right"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/mpbb2.JPG" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="right">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="right">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/i