(124, 'Sample Flat is ready at residential project- Ecovillage', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<p style="float:right;"><a class="back" href="media-news.asp?nYear=2010&amp;mon=">Back</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Sample Flat is ready at residential project- Ecovillage</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[27&nbsp;November,&nbsp;2010]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class="news">Sample Flat is ready at residential project - Ecovillage and construction is going on in full swing. <a class="email" href="http://supertechlimited.com/residential/ecovillage-noida-extension/construction-updates.asp">View</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2010-11-27 00:00:00', 0),
(125, 'Supertech Limited adopts a new corporate identity', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2010&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited adopts a new corporate identity</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[21&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2010]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>In celebration of its 50,000 customers and to rededicate itself to its customer oriented values, Supertech Limited, on 21st October 2010 introduced a change in its corporate identity. On this occasion a press conference was held at Park hotel , Delhi on 20th October.</p>\r\n<p>The new logo gives a contemporary feel with a bold S, which reflects solidity and class. Solidity of the company and its values and class for the customers who are going to make Supertech homes their abode.</p>\r\n<p>The touch of <strong>Gold</strong> in the logo indicates the <strong>richness</strong> and <strong>ever-lasting </strong>happiness,Supertech delivers&nbsp; to its valued customers.</p>\r\n<p>The <strong>Red</strong> colour denotes the <strong>Passion, Vibrancy</strong> and the <strong>Energy</strong> with which the group is re-dedicating itself to its patrons. The usage of a <strong>bold font </strong>in the logo reaffirms the company&rsquo;s permanence, commitment and the longevity of the happiness it creates for its customers. At the same time, it makes a statement about the new, youthful thinking sweeping across its ranks.</p>\r\n<p>The Tagline <strong>&lsquo;Yours for Life&rsquo; </strong>communicates the legacy of 22 successful years and gives an assurance of Good Life for Life. A promise of togetherness and ever-lasting happiness.</p>\r\n<p>Talking to media CMD R K ARORA stated that having more than 50,000 customers, a change was most certainly on the cards. A change that reflects a new dynamism and a more proactive approach towards our valued customers. Talking about the expansion plans of the company Mr. Arora said we will be soon launching two housing projects in Mumbai and Bangalore. He said company is set to get listed and raise Rs 2500 crore in the next 12 to 15 months</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2010-10-21 00:00:00', 0),
(126, 'Bhoomi pujan held at Cape Town', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2010&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Bhoomi pujan held at Cape Town</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[17&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2010]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech limited performed the bhoomi pujan of capetown project on Saturday 16 oct. 2010 the project is spread over an area of more than 50 acres in sector 74 Noida.</p>\r\n<p>Bhoomi poojan was performed by CMD<strong> Mr. R K Arora,</strong> JMD<strong> Mrs. Sangeeta Arora</strong> and Director <strong>Mr. Mohit Arora</strong>. On the auspicious occasion Sri Arora stated capetown project will have complete self cointaioned campus area built around the best of facilities where every home is designed to the most demamding standards. On this occasion singer <strong>Anuradha Paudwal</strong> sang bhajans.</p>\r\n<p>Capetown will comprises 2,3 nd 4 bhk apprtmnts in 8 different sizes. The highlights of the projects are an international level club of one lakh sq ft area of health related facilities like massage therapy center,yoga centre and medidation centre besides other attractions like waterbodies,caf&eacute; shops, sports centre with basketball,badminton,squash courts,school nd medical facilities.</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2010-10-17 00:00:00', 0);
