(127, 'Bhoomi pujan held at UpCountry', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2010&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Bhoomi pujan held at UpCountry</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[16&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2010]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited performed the Bhoomi Poojan of Upcountry project on <strong>Friday 15 oct. 2010</strong>. The project is spread over an area of 100 acres on Yamuna Expressway.Bhoomi Poojan was performed by CMD <strong>Mr.R.K.Arora</strong> , JMD <strong>Ms.Sangeeta Arora</strong> and Director Mr.<strong> Mohit Arora</strong>. On this auspicious occasion CMD Mr.R.K.Arora said that people will have a complete European experience in Spanish villas and Roman castles.Each villa is unique and captures the spirit of spain.</p>\r\n<p>Upcountry, a 100 acre integrated township on Yamuna Expressway is blessed with surroundings of pleasurable greens,man made lakes,beaches and palm trees.Besides this,there will be educational institutes,hospitals,shopping malls,hostel,gym,squash court,swimming pool etc. Spanish villas is available in size of 100 sq.yds,150 sq.yds and 200 sq.yds.while Roman castles is available in 300 sq.yds,400sq.yds and 500sq.yds.</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2010-10-16 00:00:00', 0),
