(141, 'Supertech launches ''ORB'' at Sector 74, Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2011&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech launches ''ORB'' at Sector 74, Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[28&nbsp;April,&nbsp;2011]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>First of its kind, premium round residences is yet another landmark project by Supertech Limited. The Group today announced the launch of &lsquo;ORB&rsquo; - - a unique circular-shaped, 50 storey luxurious residential development, masterminded by the renowned interior designer Twinkle Khanna.</p>\r\n<p>Innovation comes in myriad shapes. This time, its round. The first of its kind development will be built in sync with the universal symbol, the circle. This unprecedented 3 tower landmark boasts futuristic luxury homes with hi-tech automated facilities nestling amidst landscaped surroundings. The developments is been scientifically designed optimum energy efficiency and vaastu compliant construction for maximum influx of positive energy.</p>\r\n<p>Strategically located at Sector 74, Noida, ORB is a part of 50 acre integrated township project, which will comprise of 3 and 4 BHK apartments. The area of the units will range from 2215sq. ft. to 4270sq. ft. The project is been innovatively designed for maximum interior space and its circular footprint for uninterrupted supply of air and 180 degree view. Every space in this architectural opus is meticulously planned to integrate the best of aesthetics and amenities, requisite for modern lifestyles</p>\r\n<p>Elated Twinkle Khanna says, &ldquo;I am very happy to be associated to be a part of this grandeur project. I hope the interior spaces I crafted will give each of the residents a new living experience and a definitely abode which will be a class apart&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p>Twinkle appreciation with nature and aesthetics and her strongly held values echo of the walls of these residences where nothing seem to overpower.</p>\r\n<p>The developments has all the necessary amenities &amp; specifications like world-class club, swimming pool, spa, gym and sporting facilities with 100% power back up and 24X7 security.</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2011-04-28 00:00:00', 0),
