(146, 'Supertech Donates Blankets To Leprosy Patients at Kusth Ashram', ' <div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Donates Blankets To Leprosy Patients at Kusth Ashram</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[31&nbsp;December,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>As a part of company''s Corporate Social Responsibility, Supertech Limited \r\ndonated over 200 blankets today to the patients suffering from leprosy. This \r\nnoble cause was conducted by Mr. Laxman Singh Arora, Mr. K. G. Arora, Directors \r\nof Supertech.</p>\r\n<p>The blankets were donated to the patients staying at Kasturba Gram Kusth \r\nAshram, Shahadra, Delhi.</p>\r\n<p>The company, from time to time, initiates such CSR activities to contribute \r\nto the society.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ashram1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ashram2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ashram3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ashram4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n       <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ashram5.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img