(156, 'Supertech Limited And Mary Kom Come Together To Set up Boxing Academy at Upcountry', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<p style="float:right;"><a class="back" href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&amp;mon=">Back</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited And Mary Kom Come Together To Set up Boxing Academy at Upcountry</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[26&nbsp;November,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech Limited comes together with MC Mary Kom, the London Olympics 2012 Bronze medalist, to set a world class Boxing Academy at Upcountry, Yamuna Expressway. The academy will be the first of its kind in Noida &amp; Greater Noida.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The MC Mary Kom Boxing Academy will be set up in 100 acre township at Upcountry, Yamuna Expressway. The academy will be the first of its kind in Noida &amp; Greater Noida. The academy will cater to numerous aspiring boxers, who were till date deprived of such world class academies in their own vicinity. Mary Kom will be a guiding force behind this academy and will help the youth of nurture their talent in the sport.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the event, the company had invited its customers to enjoy the fun filled day with Mary Kom.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="720">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/boxerth1.jpg" /></td>\r\n			<td align="right"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/boxerth2.jpg" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td align="right">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/boxerth3.jpg" /></td>\r\n			<td align="right"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/boxerth4.jpg" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2012-11-26 00:00:00', 0),
