(158, 'Supertech Organises Celebration Week at Pentagon Mall', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Organises Celebration Week at Pentagon Mall</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[25&nbsp;November,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited has organized a ''Celebration Week'' at The Pentagon Mall-Haridwar''s \r\nfirst and biggest Mall cum Multiplex. The company announced the commencement of \r\nthis gala week at a press conference on November 25, ''12. The celebration week \r\nis an extension to the festive season, full of joy, shopping at hefty discounts \r\nand attractive prizes. The celebration week which has started from 25th November \r\nwill continue till December 2nd with each day offering different theme to the \r\nvisitors along with variety of related attractions for the day. The week will \r\ninclude theme based activities for specific days. &quotCreative Day&quot on November \r\n27th, which will be followed by Fun Day, Utsav Day, Family Day and Celebration \r\nDay in the coming days. The week promises to provide a day full of fun, \r\ncelebration and togetherness along with best of the offers for visitors to \r\nenhance their shopping experience at the Pentagon Mall.</p>\r\n<p>The celebrations at the ''Celebration Day'' began with a Lamp Lighting \r\nCeremony. The day also included Magic Show, Live Band performances and lots \r\nmore. It was a win-win situation for the visitors as they got numerous discounts \r\nfrom the retailers and a day full of enjoyment. The company also announced the \r\ninclusion of new brands in the Mall. The new brands will include names like Ritu \r\nWears - Big Life, Reliance Trends, DLF brand among others. </p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/celebration-week1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/celebration-week2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/celebration-week3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-11-25 00:00:00', 0),
(159, 'Karabi press conference', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Karabi press conference</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[23&nbsp;November,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited in collaboration with Karabi Artworks organised a press \r\nconference today to announce the commencement of art week starting from 24th \r\nNovember to December 2nd 2012 at the Supernova site in Sector 94, Noida. The art \r\nweek brings forth a platform for aspiring artists to showcase their artworks. It \r\nwill bestow the society with visual and performing arts, which will have \r\nprofound effect on people.</p>\r\n<p>The week long art exhibition will display art works from Partha Shaw, Suchit \r\nSahni, Saurav Bhattacharya, H Barre, Rajeev Mondal, Sanjib Gagoi, Prassana \r\nKashyap, Suresh Kumar Achari, Purnna Behera, Neeraj Gupta and Swayamprabha \r\nParida. There will be around 25-30 great pieces of art and sculpture from across \r\nthe country.&nbsp </p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/soniath1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/soniath2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/soniath3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/soniath4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-11-23 00:00:00', 0),
(160, 'Supertech Limited And The Leela Palaces, Hotels and Resorts Announce New Project In Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited And The Leela Palaces, Hotels and Resorts  Announce New Project In Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[31&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>North India''s leading real estate developer, Supertech Limited and the world-class award winning hotel chain, The Leela \r\nPalaces, Hotels and Resorts today signed a Memorandum of Understanding (MOU) for \r\nthe iconic luxury hotel - The Leela Palace Noida, at Supernova, Noida. Supertech \r\nwill construct and develop the property which will be operated and managed by \r\nThe Leela.</p>\r\n<p>The new hotel named The Leela Palace Noida will be situated in one of the \r\nfive towers of Supernova - India''s tallest and largest mixed use development \r\nlocated in Sector 94, Noida. The property will be an ultra luxurious hotel which \r\nwill comprise of approximately 250 exquisitely appointed guest rooms and suits, \r\nsuperlative restaurants, lounges, banquet facilities, internationally renowned \r\nspa and modern fitness centre. In keeping with The Leela''s high standards of \r\nexcellence, the hotel will offer exclusive services for corporates. According to \r\nMr. R K Arora, Chairman &amp Managing Director, Supertech Limited, &quotSupernova is an \r\nepitome of luxury and class and The Leela is also known for its opulent \r\nproperties. This amalgamation of two premium brands will a connoisseurs'' \r\ndestination with the best facilities and features to offer&quot. </p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/leela1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/leela2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/leela3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/leela4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-10-31 00:00:00', 0),
(161, 'Air Ballooning at Upcountry site', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Air Ballooning at Upcountry site</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[26&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech organized a 3 day event on October 26, 27 &amp 28 at its Upcountry \r\nproject site at Yamuna Expressway. The event saw participation of huge chunks of \r\npeople, enjoying the hot air balloon ride, simultaneously viewing the progress \r\nhappening on the project site. The event also had activities like zorbing and \r\npara gliding. The company had invited all Upcountry customers and their families \r\nto enjoy the three days of fun and festivity.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/baloon1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/baloon2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/baloon3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/baloon4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/baloon5.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/baloon6.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n   