(163, 'Supertech Limited gave possession of plots at ''Upcountry'', Yamuna Expressway', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited gave possession of plots at ''Upcountry'', Yamuna Expressway</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[20&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited gave possession of plots at Ã¢â‚¬ËœUpcountryÃ¢â‚¬â„¢, Yamuna Expressway \r\non October 20, ''12. On the occasion, Mr. R.K. Arora, CMD of Supertech handed \r\nover the possession letters to the proud owners. Mr. Mohit Arora, Director of \r\nSupertech, key officials of the company and around 400 families of Upcountry \r\nwitnessed the occasion.</p>\r\n<p>Supertech delivered plots of sizes 100 sq. yd, 150 sq. yd. and 200 sq. yd. \r\nand expect to deliver the entire 100 acre township in the next 3 years. \r\nUpcountry plots is the first possession of any developer on Yamuna Expressway \r\nand also it is only development which has all the plans approved by the \r\nAuthority for constructing a project on Yamuna Expressway. </p>\r\n<p>The handing over ceremony was followed by performances of Ã¢â‚¬ËœBand of BoysÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ who \r\nsung the foot tapping songs one after the other and kept the enthusiastic crowd \r\non its toes. The kids also had a gala time with various sporting and games \r\noptions available for them.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/upcer-th1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/upcer-th2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n    