(178, 'Zee News My Earth My Duty : Plantation Drive at Eco Village - II, Noida Extn.', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Zee News My Earth My Duty : Plantation Drive at Eco Village - II, Noida Extn.</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[8&nbsp;September,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Zee news initiated Ã¢â‚¬Å“ My Earth My DutyÃ¢â‚¬Â plantation drive and painting \r\ncompetition culminated at Supertech Eco Village II site. On this occasion Mr. \r\nMohit Arora, Director Supertech planted sapling &amp briefed about the plantation \r\ndrive. More than 300 customers who were present on this occasion participated in \r\nthe programme. A dozen kids participated in the painting competition and won \r\nprizes. Supertech Limited was the principal sponsor of &quotMy Earth My Duty&quot an \r\ninitiative from Zee News to create awareness towards environment. The campaign \r\nstarted with sapling plantation by former President of India, Dr. APJ Abdul \r\nKalam. The initiative was organized in 30 cities across India which had \r\nparticipation from 50 million youngsters from the country.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/zned-th1.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/zned-th2.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/zned-th3.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/zned-th4.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/zned-th5.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\