(187, 'Supertech Launched Supernova Spira Residences In Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Launched Supernova Spira Residences In Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[27&nbsp;August,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech has launched its prestigious project- Supernova Spira Residences at \r\nSector 94 Noida. The launch also witnessed the outstanding performance by \r\ncomedian PAPA CJ and enthralling dance performances by various dance groups. \r\nMaserati officials were also present in this occasion.</p>\r\n<p>Spira stands at a height of 300 metres and comprises of 80 floors amongst \r\nwhich 13 floors are dedicated for the residential apartments. Fully furnished, \r\nvaastu friendly units spanning over an area of 3,200 sq. ft. to 4,000 sq. ft. \r\nare designed to ensure maximum utilization of the usable area. These high end \r\npremium apartments are priced between Rs. 5 crores to 7 crores.</p>\r\n<p>As Mr. R K Arora, Chairman &amp Managing Director, Supertech Limited, says, \r\n&quotSpira is a premium product made with the amalgamation of world''s best names in \r\nthe fields of architecture, design and engineering. Spira Residences is one of \r\nthe most high-end products of the company and in and around Noida offering \r\nunmatched features&quot.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/supernova-spira-th1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/supernova-spira-th2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://