(195, 'Supertech and Network18 organized NOIDA10K - Run ko Banao Fun on July 08, 2012', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech and Network18 organized NOIDA10K - Run ko Banao Fun on July 08, 2012</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[9&nbsp;July,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Over the years Noida has grown to become the greatest business hub and a \r\nhighly favored destination. People from all spheres of life have found their \r\ncalling in this city. Be it students exploring educational institutes for \r\nfurther studies, aspiring businessmen searching for opportunities or for people \r\nlooking for a home, Noida has emerged as a one stop destination. To pay tribute \r\nto this flourishing city, Supertech Limited and Network18 hosted a marathon, \r\n''Noida10k'' - Run Ko Banao Fun. Noida10k was the first ever run in the city.</p>\r\n<p>As Noida is one of the fastest developing cities of India and has gained the \r\nstatus of a highly preferred city, the run was the perfect time for the people \r\nwho have always believed in it to RUN for it, to give the city what it deserves. \r\nThe theme of the Noida10k run was to "Run for clean, green and safe Noida", \r\n"strong and healthy Noida".</p>\r\n<p>The Noida10k run happened on July 8, 2012 in the heart of Noida at the \r\nRamleela Ground, Sec 21A. The run was a joint effort of around 8000 people from \r\nacross the country, majorly from Noida and neighboring regions, institutions and \r\nassociations who have partnered to make it a grand event. Actors Tushar Kapoor, \r\nUdita Goswami, Nigar Khan and Model Geeta Basra were present at the run.</p>\r\n<p>The run had 5 categories - Elite, Open - with chip and without chip, \r\nCorporate and Fun Run.</p>\r\n<p>There were a total of 10 prizes each in the Elite Men open and Elite Women \r\nopen categories. The total prize money for Elite Men open 10 km category was Rs. \r\n1,00,000 and the total prize money for Elite Women Open is Rs. 75000.</p>\r\n<p>Mr. R.K. Arora, Chariman &amp Managing Director of Supertech Limited flagged off \r\nthe run and gave away the prizes to the winners.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-1.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-2.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-3.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-4.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-5.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-6.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-7.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-8.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-9.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-10.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-11.jpg" alt=""></td>\r\n		<td>\r\n		<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NOIDA10K-12.jpg" alt=""></td>\r