(196, 'Supertech forays in Millennium City', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech forays in Millennium City</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[4&nbsp;June,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited known for launching and delivering its grandeur projects in  cities such as Noida, Greater Noida, Ghaziabad, Meerut, Moradabad, Haridwar and  Rudrapur, now enters the millennium city, Gurgaon, Haryana. The company launched  its first project in Gurgaon, christened Araville in Sector 79. Araville is a  premium residential project situated on the foothills of Aravalli hills. The  project is spread over an area of around 10 acres comprising 2, 3 and 4 BHK  units. This artistically designed project will be laced with all ultra-modern  facilities, club house, tennis court, swimming pool, Golf Park, dedicated kids  zones all set amidst beautiful landscapes. The project is in close proximity of  shopping malls, schools, offices and medical institutions.</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-06-04 00:00:00', 0),
(197, 'Supertech associates with Hindustan-Hindustan Times Uttar Pradesh Development Conclave in Lucknow', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech associates with Hindustan-Hindustan Times Uttar Pradesh Development Conclave in Lucknow</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[26&nbsp;May,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>For the advancement and improvement of the state of Uttar Pradesh, a month  long campaign, &quot<em>Suniye Mukhyamantri ji, Humare Shaher ki Awaaz</em> was held in the  state with a series of activities. Hindustan invited letters from the people of  the state asking them to bring forth the issues which were a hindrance in the  development and needed redressal. This will form the basis of the development of  the state government for the next 5 years. The campaign was culminated in a  conclave held in Lucknow on May 26, ''12, where Supertech Limited was the  principal and sole sponsor. The conclave had the presence of Honorable Chief  Minister of Uttar Pradesh, Sri Akhilesh Yadav, Dr. A P J Abdul Kalam, Former  President of India, Minister of HRD, Communication and IT, Government of India,  Sri Kapil Sibal and the Director of Supertech Limited, Mr. Mohit Arora. On the  occasion, Mr. Mohit Arora also presented a momento to Mr. Ahkilesh Yadav.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/akhilesh-yadav3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td><img border="0" align="right" src=" http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/akhilesh-yadav1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/akhilesh-yadav2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-05-26 00:00:00', 0),
(198, 'Supertech Performs Bhoomi Poojan Of ''Golf Country-Villas''', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Performs Bhoomi Poojan Of ''Golf Country-Villas''</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[7&nbsp;April,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited performed the bhoomi poojan of Golf Country &ndash; Villas today.  The ceremony marked the commencement of construction of the villas located at Yamuna Expressway.</p>\r\n<p>The bhoomi poojan was performed by Mrs. Sangeeta Arora, Joint Managing Director, Mr. Mohit Arora, Director, Supertech Limited. The occasion was attended by the customers and officials of Supertech Group.</p>\r\n<p>Speaking on the occasion, Mr RK Arora said, &ldquo;We have always believed in offering something different to our customers, so with the construction of villas, we have tried to provide a healthy and relaxed living in the surroundings of a golf course and amidst green environment.&rdquo;It is planned as` modern urban development in concept of live,work,play and learn.</p>\r\n<p>&quot;The residents of the project can enjoy many locational advantages as it has wide open roads, well defined sector areas and pre-planned infrastructure giving a worth to this location. Besides these, Yamuna Expressway has tremendous scope because of its great connectivity like the proposed metro link, very soon to be operational Yamuna Expressway and the International Airport, which will be just 15min away. Yamuna Expressway will be a tourist attraction in the future as it also boasts of F1 track&rdquo;, added Mr. Arora. Yamuna expressway will shorten distance to Agra and provide a gateway to india&rsquo;s tourist corridor.Yamuna Expressway has direct access from DND toll bridge. Infact, Formula 1 event has brought international fame to this area. Yamuna Expressway area is attaining national fame as area of education excellence through establishment of Gautam Budh University. The opening of Yamuna Expressway shall provide a trigger to real estate prices in this area.The possession of Golf Country - Villas will be given in 24 months.</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-04-07 00:00:00', 0),
(199, 'SupertechÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Another Year of Glorious Association with Rajasthan Royals', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">SupertechÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Another Year of Glorious Association with Rajasthan Royals</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[4&nbsp;April,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>The extended association of <strong>Supertech Limited</strong> for the consecutive second year with Rajasthan Royals in the fifth season of the T20 IPL was again another remarkable moments with all the highs, lows and the undefeatable team spirit and attitude.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe main objective of the association is to leverage the team image which has a great combination of young, energetic and experienced cricketers as it reflects the company&rsquos ideology as pioneer, dynamic and youthful.<br />\r\n&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp <br />\r\nThe company has the association with the team since last year (IPL-season four). Cricket is a religion in India so the association was definitely also for the love of the game. The company always believes in delivering the best of products and services, so the association with Rajasthan Royals was for the obvious reason, the first champion of IPL T20. The Rajasthan Royals team players were sporting Supertech branded uniform.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCommenting on the brand''s association with Rajasthan Royals IPL team, Mr. R. K Arora, CMD, Supertech Limited, said, &quotThe main reason for our association with Rajasthan Royals was because of the believing in the same philosophy. The RR team comprises of lot of young new talents and experienced world class players. And our ideology is also to promote new talent which brings a lot of fresh new innovative ideas and the same is implemented with the support of the experienced team members.&quot</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-04-04 00:00:00', 0),
(200, 'Supernova, Sector 94, Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supernova, Sector 94, Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[20&nbsp;February,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><ul>\r\n    <li>Project Advisors: Knight Frank ,London.</li>\r\n    <li>Landscape Consultants: Cracknell, Dubai</li>\r\n    <li>Concept and Architecture: Benoy London.</li>\r\n    <li>Structural Consultant and MEP- Buro Happold,UK</li>\r\n    <li>Consultants: RWDI ,Canada.</li>\r\n    <li>Geotechnical Engineers- Golder Associates, Australia.</li>\r\n    <li>Construction Advisor- Brookfield Multiplex, Australia.</li>\r\n    <li>Engineers and Contractors &ndash; B.L. Kashyap, India</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>India&rsquo;s Tallest Mixed-use Development. Located in Noida, just 0 km. from  Delhi</p>\r\n<p>This grandeur landmark is all set to take shape at Sector 94, Noida. Graced  with luxurious modern conveniences, this LEED Platinum certified fully  integrated urban oasis is designed to be the nerve centre of NCR. Come, be a  part of this auspicious occasion that marks the dawn of construction of your new  world.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<p>- Spread over 5 million square feet of area. The biggest and tallest  mixed-use development of India.</p>\r\n<p>- Features Spira, an iconic 80-storey superstructure.</p>\r\n<p>- Architectural success rests on world-renowned London based architects,  Benoy.</p>\r\n<p>- Houses 2 luxury hotels, premium and luxury malls, futuristic offices, serviced suites and ultra luxurious condos.</p>\r\n<p>-In close proximity to South Delhi. Well connected through DND, Noida  Expressway, the Metro link and the proposed Kalindi Kunj 8-lane Expressway</p>\r\n<p>-First-of-its-kind water front development in this region with Vaastu-inspired super structures and panoramic views of the bird sanctuary</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-02-20 00:00:00', 0),
(201, 'Supertech Celebrated Foundation Completion Ceremony of ''North Eye'' - North India''s tallest residential development', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Celebrated Foundation Completion Ceremony of ''North Eye'' - North India''s tallest residential development</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[12&nbsp;February,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>With much excitement, happiness and entertainment, Supertech Limited celebrated the Foundation Completion Ceremony of one of its kind grandeur project &lsquo;North Eye&rsquo;. The project is North India&rsquo;s tallest residential development. Standing at 255 meters with 66 floors, the project is strategically located at Sector 74, Noida.</p>\r\n<p>The construction at North Eye has witnessed one of the deepest piling activities of India. Soil investigation activities were conducted by a team of experts from one of the reputed civil engineering company &ndash; Langan International of U.S.A  . Besides, high-rise constructions like North Eye require expert designing to combat wind pressure at high altitudes, so wind tunnel experts RWDI from UK have been hired as consulting partners to test the stability of the structure in windy conditions. The entire building will be reinforced with 17,000 MT of steel and 1,23,000 cu.m. of  concrete. Strategically designed by VMS Mumbai, the apartments are spacious, well ventilated and provides all the modern facilities and amenities which will set a different experience of living for its residents.</p>\r\n<p>Spread over an area of 21 lakh sq.ft. built up, innovatively designed, North Eye is being built up in four parts - East wing, West wing, North Wing and Central Tower. North Eye boasts of an impeccable fusion of avant-garde architecture and expert craftsmanship.</p>\r\n<p>On the occasion, Mr. R.K. Arora, CMD Supertech Limited said, &ldquo;We are very delighted to complete the foundation with 160 ft. depth piles of our iconic project &lsquo;North Eye, the future resides are now a step closer towards the dream of living closer to the moon.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>On the occasion, Mr. R.K. Arora, CMD Supertech Limited said, &ldquo;We are very delighted to complete the foundation with 160 ft. depth piles of our iconic project &lsquo;North Eye, the future resides are now a step closer towards the dream of living closer to the moon.&rdquo;</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-02-12 00:00:00', 0),
(202, 'Supertech Performs Bhoomi Pujan of the Grandeur Project ''Supernova''', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2012&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Performs Bhoomi Pujan of the Grandeur Project ''Supernova''</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[29&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2012]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited, a leading real estate developer performed the bhoomi pujan of the grandeur project <strong>&lsquo;Supernova&rsquo;</strong> which is <strong>North India&rsquo;s biggest mixed-use development </strong>spread across 5 million sq. ft. of area. The project has five towers amongst which <strong>&lsquo;Spira&rsquo;</strong> &ndash; The Iconic Tower is <strong>India&rsquo;s tallest mixed use development </strong>having 80 floors which stands at 300 meters.</p>\r\n<p>The puja ceremony was performed by Mr. R.K. Arora, Chairman &amp; Managing Director, Mrs. Sangeeta Arora, Joint Managing Director and Mr. Mohit Arora, Director, Supertech Limited. The occasion was also attended by the customers and officials of Supertech Group.</p>\r\n<p>On the auspicious occasion of bhoomi pujan, Mr. RK Arora said, &ldquo;The mixed use development will be a landmark project in North India, and I hope, it will set a different experience of living for its residents. The project is a unique combination of residences, service apartments, hotels, shopping malls, office spaces and recreational centers, which has five state-of-the-art world class towers.&quot;</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2012-01-29 00:00:00', 0),
(203, 'CREDAI Members Visit to Supertech''s Precast Factory', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">CREDAI Members Visit to Supertech''s Precast Factory</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[12&nbsp;December,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>On December 12th, a group of around 100 CREDAI (Confederation of Real Estate DevelopersÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ Associations of India) members from all across the country visited SupertechÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Precast manufacturing unit Ã¢â‚¬Å“SupercastÃ¢â‚¬Â in Ecotech-16, Greater Noida. The objective of the visit was to showcase a unique construction technology created by Supertech.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A skilled team of 20 engineers from Supertech escorted the CREDAI members to the factory, which is spread over an area of 60,000 sq. mtrs. and made them acquainted with the operations of the unit. They also briefed the members about the benefits and advantages of using such a technology. The members were very delighted to experience the tech know-how of the precast construction process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After the elaborate guided tour, photographs were taken of all the members, which were presented to them as memento by Supertech, at the culmination of their visit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Mohit Arora, Director of the company addressed the CREDAI members and took them through a visual shoot displaying the construction of a building with the use of precast technology. Thereafter, a presentation was run which further elaborated the companyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s new technology. This was followed by a Q&A session with Mr. Mohit Arora and other key officials of the company.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="center">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/cr.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            \r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-12-12 00:00:00', 0),
(204, 'Supertech comes to USA at India Property Expo', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech comes to USA at India Property Expo</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[9&nbsp;November,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>SUPERTECH, THE MOST PROGRESSIVE REAL ESTATE GROUP NOW COMES TO YOUR CITY. </p>\r\n\r\n <p>You love your soil and we understand that. Therefore, Supertech has taken the initiative to cross those extra miles and cover the distance for you. We shall be right there in your city to assist and update you on the multiple opportunities with Supertech in NCR. Thus, making every step of your investment convenient and memorable.  </p>\r\n\r\n <p>It''s the perfect time to invest in NCR, where property appreciation is over 35% P.A.</p>\r\n<p>They say the wise grabs an opportunity while the time is ripe. And that time is now, when the dollar is soaring at an all time high. The perfect time to grab hold of an opportunity that lies in NCR where property appreciation is over 35% p.a. With none other than Supertech. The Group that''s on a relentless mission to change the skyline of NCR for the last 25 years with over 36 projects.</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-11-09 00:00:00', 0),
(205, 'Grand Opening of Shopprix Mall: Enjoyment, Entertainment & Excitement', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Grand Opening of Shopprix Mall: Enjoyment, Entertainment & Excitement</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[18&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited launched most awaited Shopprix Mall in Meerut on October 18th 2013. Event started with ribbon cutting ceremony by Chairman & Managing Director Mr. RK Arora, Mr. Mohit Arora and other Directors lit the lamp and marked the inauguration of the Mall. Press Conference was held where entire Meerut media was invited. </p>\r\n\r\n <p>Afternoon witnessed huge crowd enjoying and shaking legs on peppy numbers played by DJ. Couples and kids were invited on the stage for performance which was truly a dose of entertainment for general public. </p>\r\n\r\n <p>Evening was filled with entertainment where special arrangements were made for Elite guests. Performance by dance troupe created joyful ambience. Emcee Madhukar Malhotra did a wonderful job by entertaining and engaging the crowd in fun-filled activities for all age groups. Gifts and complementary coupons were also distributed and evening concluded with a performance by Carnation band.</p>\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/sm.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/sm1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/sm2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/sm3.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/sm4.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/sm6.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-10-18 00:00:00', 0),
(206, 'Supertech launches Shopprix Mall- Meerut''s Biggest Shopping Destination', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech launches Shopprix Mall- Meerut''s Biggest Shopping Destination</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[17&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited, one of the leading real estate developers of North India, has launched Shopprix Mall which is the biggest shopping destination of Meerut. Meerut spells unbelievable opportunity for those in the retail business and Shopprix Mall will help businesses harness this opportunity. Located right on Delhi- Meerut Hapur Bypass road, it is a hub of shopping, dining, entertainment and hospitality, with stunning multi level structure that houses a host of brands across categories to cater to a high influx of visitors, all year round.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A- first-of-its-kind in scale and size, a host of facilities and never before features makes it the core of business opportunity for investors in this region. Shopprix mall has 3,80,000 sq ft of gross leasable area with a beautiful facade and wide display windows.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shopprix mall is home to some of the biggest brands with a large area for retail shopping dedicated to high fashion, lifestyle, electronics to home furnishings, accessories and a lot more. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The third floor at Shopprix Mall features a sprawling food court with a delicious fare of dining options for each shopper. Multi cuisine outlets, takeaways and fine dining restaurants make for a truly buzzing ambience for visitors across all age groups. Additionally, a 3-screen multiplex provides the perfect place for entertainment for the whole family.</p>\r\n</p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-10-17 00:00:00', 0),
(207, 'Supertech Won "Developer of The Year" & "Leader of The Year" Awards by Hundred Communications For Its Excellence In Indian Real Estate Industry', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Won "Developer of The Year" & "Leader of The Year" Awards by Hundred Communications For Its Excellence In Indian Real Estate Industry</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[28&nbsp;September,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited, on Sep 28 evening received awards at a grand event organized by Hundred Communications at The Crystal Hall, The Lait, New Delhi. Excellence and innovation in projects to luxury residential and CSR initiatives by Realty Developers were the various categories to judge the parameters for the selection process. For its immense contribution to the Indian real estate industry and constructing the luxurious and high rise buildings, Supertech Limited received 2 awards under the "Innovative & Luxury Residentials" category.                    Mr. Rajeev Rai Director Sales & Marketing, Supertech Limited received both the awards. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n <p>The Property Awards was held to recognize and applaud excellence in Indian real estate industry. The award function was followed by launch of books- Indian Realty Yearbook - a book on luxury real estate and Real Leaders which is about CSR leaders in real estate. </p>\r\n <p>The evening saw the presence of all top real estate developers, interior designers & architects from all across the country.</p>\r\n <p>To honor the winners, Mr. Vijender Singh, Chitrangda Singh & Soha Ali Khan was invited as Chief Guests for the evening.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/Indian-real-estate-industry1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/Indian-real-estate-industry3.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/Indian-real-estate-industry2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/Indian-real-estate-industry4.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-09-28 00:00:00', 0),
(208, 'Supertech shines at IRF 2013', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n<p style="float:right;"><a class="back" href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&amp;mon=">Back</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech shines at IRF 2013</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:12px!important;">[27&nbsp;September,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>India Retail Forum (IRF) - An annual platform where the bests in the retail fraternity from all over the world meet, greet, exhibit and celebrate their commercial prowess. With 3000+ participants, 100+ exhibitors, 300+ speakers, IRF is unarguably India&#39;s largest retail exhibition connecting retailers to real estate developers, brands to innovation, and retail support firms to cutting-edge technologies. The event awards the achievements of India&#39;s best performing and most innovative retail brands, companies and concepts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This year, the two-day India Retail Forum 2013, was held at the Mumbai&#39;s Renaissance Hotel on September 25th and 26th.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With an objective to create a niche in the retail segment, Supertech Group showcased its shining retail projects in Powai Hall, at Renaissance Hotel. Understanding the potential and the opportunities tier - 2 cities hold, the focus was on the shining stars of Meerut, Haridwar and Rudrapur - Shopprix Mall, Pentagon Mall and Metropolis Mall respectively. While the Pentagon Mall at SIDCUL, Haridwar boasts of the largest commercial complex in Uttrakhand, the Shopprix Mall has been awarded with the Best Upcoming Destination of NCR by Estate Avenue - a leading retail magazine and lastly, the Metropolis Mall that boasts of being the first and largest retail mall in the Kumaon region. All these commercial destinations have been a favored choice of customers and a host to international and national brands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What&#39;s more, besides these retail havens, Supertech has made its retail presence felt at other places as well. The expected number of footfalls at Radiance Mall and Aurora at Noida, will bear true testimony to Supertech&#39;s increasing clout in the retail sphere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All these remarkable retail destinations were showcased at the IRF 2013 and gained much anticipated attention of the exhibitors and participants.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 1, '2013-09-27 00:00:00', 0),
