(213, 'NDTV Felicitated Supertech For Its Excellence And Innovation In Indian Real Estate Industry', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">NDTV Felicitated Supertech For Its Excellence And Innovation In Indian Real Estate Industry</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[4&nbsp;June,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited, on June 3 evening received an award at a gala event organized by NDTV at Durbar Hall, Taj Palace, New Delhi. The Property Awards was held for the first time to recognize and applaud excellence in Indian real estate and to set the most credible benchmark for the industry. The evening saw the presence of all top real estate developers from all across the country.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>To honor the winners, Mr. Ajay Maken, Honorable Minister of Housing and Urban Poverty Alleviation was invited as Chief Guest for the evening.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>There were various categories to judge the parameters and to choose the best amongst it. For its immense contribution to the Indian real estate industry, tie-ups with international brands like Disney and Armani and for launching and constructing the luxurious and high rise buildings, Supertech Limited received an award under the "Innovative Leadership" category. Mr. R.K. Arora, Chairman & Managing Director, Supertech Limited was present to receive the award.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NDTV-Awards1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NDTV-Awards2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NDTV-Awards3.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NDTV-Awards4.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NDTV-Awards5.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/NDTV-Awards6.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-06-04 00:00:00', 0),
(214, 'Disney India ties-up with Supertech for Disney themed Interiors & Exteriors', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Disney India ties-up with Supertech for Disney themed Interiors & Exteriors</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[24&nbsp;April,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited announced its association with Disney India for Disney inspired interiors and exteriors at company''s proposed residential project, Fable Castle, part of an integrated township, Golf Country, located at Yamuna Expressway, Greater Noida.<br />\r\n&nbsp<br />\r\nThis association will provide an opportunity to kids and families to bring their favorite Disney characters to life. Disney fans can choose from their favourite Disney stories or their beloved Disney characters and own family spaces that are colourful, timeless and inspiring.</p>\r\n<p>On the occasion, Mr. R. K. Arora, Chairman and Managing Director, Supertech Limited said, &ampldquoWe are really happy to announce our tie up with Disney India. Disney characters and stories have inspired every generation and this will give an opportunity to all those who want to have a Disney magic in their homes. As a company, we have always tried to give something different and new to our valued customers and this time again we are creating an all together different project. We are the first ones in North India to bring this unique concept in housing&amprdquo.<br />\r\n&nbsp<br />\r\n&ampldquoWe are thrilled to work with Supertech and offer Indian families an opportunity to bring a piece of Disney magic into their homes. Through our association with Supertech, we look forward to bringing Disney inspired home environments and d&eacutecor to kids and families in India&amprdquo, said Roshini Bakshi, managing director, Consumer Products, Retail and Publishing, Disney UTV. &ampldquoWe work towards bring alive Disney stories and characters in the form of compelling products and experiences. Our Disney Home products span across total home solutions including furniture, bedding, rugs, tableware, kitchenware, fans, paints and bath accessories&amprdquo, she added.<br />\r\n&nbsp<br />\r\nSpread over an area of 7.5 acres, the project will have around 1000 apartments that will have rooms inspired by Disney stories and characters.<br />\r\n&nbsp<br />\r\nDisney home products span across total home solutions including furniture, bedding, rugs, tableware, kitchenware, fans, paints and bath accessories. The project will have Disney-inspired rooms consisting of Disney-branded furnishing, home d&eacutecor products, colour palettes and more, bringing alive a complete Disney experience to families. It will also have Disney-inspired recreational areas such as, an exclusive Children&amprsquos Club with a themed swimming pool, play zone and many other Disney characters inspired amenities, for the children to spend time with their family and to bond together.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/disney-evnt1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/disney-evnt2.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">\r\n			From L2R-Mr. Mohit Arora, MD,Supertech Ltd, Mr. \r\n			R.K.Arora,CMD,Supertech Ltd,Ms. Roshni Bakshi, MD,Consumer \r\n			Products,Retail&ampPublishing, Disney UTV</td>\r\n            <td valign="top">\r\n            From L2R-Mr. Mohit Arora, MD,Supertech Ltd, Mr. \r\n			R.K.Arora,CMD,Supertech Ltd-addressing the media</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-04-24 00:00:00', 0),
(215, 'Supertech presents NDTV Business Leadership Awards.', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech presents NDTV Business Leadership Awards.</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[8&nbsp;April,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech was the principal sponsor of NDTV Profit Business Leadership Awards 2012 that took place on April 8, ''13 at Hyatt Regency, Delhi. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The occasion saw the presence of all top shots from various industries - Banking, Housing, Aviation, Telecom, Automobile, Information Technology, etc. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. R.K. Arora, Chairman & Managing Director of Supertech gave away prizes in two categories - Banking and Business Leader of The Year. Mr. Rajender Sehgal, Group Head - Institutional Banking, PSUs, Government Business and Custody, HDFC Bank received an award from Mr. Arora in Banking category and Mr. Anand Mahindra, Chairman & Managing Director, Mahindra & Mahindra for Business Leader of the Year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The event also graced the presence of Dr. Montek Singh Ahluwalia, Deputy Chairman of the Planning Commission for India.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ndtv-th1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ndtv-th2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n       <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ndtv-th3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ndtv-th4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n   \r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ndtv-th5.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ndtv-th6.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ndtv-th7.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            </td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-04-08 00:00:00', 0),
(216, 'Supertech Limited Gifted Vehicles & Electronic Devices to Okhla Bird Sanctuary For Better Surveillance & Protection of the Sanctuary', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited Gifted Vehicles & Electronic Devices to Okhla Bird Sanctuary For Better Surveillance & Protection of the Sanctuary</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[29&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited is known for significantly contributing to the social cause for the upliftment of society. The company has now taken a pledge through an instrumental initiative to conserve and protect wildlife. It today marked the beginning of a great initiative by giving away gifts to Okhla Bird Sanctuary for wild life conservation, protection and awareness at the sanctuary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech gifted vehicles, like Gypsy, Motor Bikes, Cycles and electronic devices such as Laptop, LCD Projector and Porta Cabin on this occasion. The gift also included PVC Chairs etc. to meet the urgent needs of the Okhla Bird Sanctuary to better the efforts to protect wildlife in the sanctuary. These gifts were presented to Mr. B. Prabhakar, Divisional Forest Officer of Gautam Buddha Nagar by Mr. A.K. Jain, Director-Projects of the company, at a function held at Supernova site. </p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n       <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n   \r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs5.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs6.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs7.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs8.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/bs9.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            \r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-01-29 00:00:00', 0),
(217, 'Supertech Launched River Crest - A Grand Township at Rudrapur', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Launched River Crest - A Grand Township at Rudrapur</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[13&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited, one of the leading real estate developers of North India, today announced the launch of a creation crafted in the finest of luxury, River Crest in Rudrapur, Udham Singh Nagar. The township will feature development of Villas and Residential Apartments to meet the different demands of people of Rudrapur. The villas will have a unique concept and will be made along with river stream, which is also going to be developed by Supertech Limited. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Idealized in the SIDCUL area of Rudrapur on the National Highway - 87, River Crest dignifies the beauty of luxury living for elites coveting a rich moment to announce their arrival in life. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spread in the area of 24 acres, River Crest offers 196 plots with areas ranging from 150 - 350 square yards and 97 villas with plot area options ranging from 250 - 500 square yards, which will provide an ultra exclusive neighborhood to the elite residents of this luxury township. The project has best amenities in offer and provides great connectivity to the key destinations. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speaking on the occasion Mr. R.K. Arora, CMD, Supertech Limited said, Ã¢â‚¬Å“I am delighted to announce our new project in Rudrapur. This township is a part of companyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s prestigious project in the regionÃ¢â‚¬Â. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ã¢â‚¬Å“The township will offer a unique experience to the buyers and will further boost the real estate market in the region and also enhance the confidence of the investors and the buyers. With best of the facilities and easy connectivity, the region will also attract the corporates and industries making the region a perfect real estate avenueÃ¢â‚¬Â, added Mr. R.K. Arora.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>River Crest, one of the self-possessed destinations discerned on the Rampur-Nainital Highway, is an inspiring river side township. Amidst natural undulating green carpet, Rivercrest is adorned with a sparkling river flowing through it. Being surrounded with landscaped garden, surfacing trees and exuberant forests, the view Rivercrest beckons is awe-inspiring, enrapturing in a feeling close to divine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The project features best of the amenities including 24X7 power backup, round the clock security, centralized controlled room for the entire security management, electronic surveillance through CCTV cameras, a fully dedicated play area for kids and a club to enjoy best of the living among others. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/rclaunch1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right"><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/rclaunch2.jpg" alt="" />\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n   \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-01-13 00:00:00', 0),
(218, 'Lohri Celebrations At Cape Town, Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Lohri Celebrations At Cape Town, Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[12&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>On the occasion of Lohri, Supertech has organized a two-day long festivity at its Cape Town site at Sector 74, Noida. The Lohri celebrations will be on from 10am and go on till 5 pm. The company has invited around 200 customers and their families to be a part of this festivity. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>To create an aura of Lohri, the site is decorated based on the theme of the festival. The guests can also enjoy special performances by bhangra and dhol artists. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also, not to forget LohriÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s main attraction, rewari and peanuts which are served to the people who visit.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/carniwal1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n   \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-01-12 00:00:00', 0),
(219, 'Winter Carnival at Upcountry, Greater Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2013&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Winter Carnival at Upcountry, Greater Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[12&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2013]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech has organized a Winter Carnival on January 12th and 13th 2013 at its Upcountry site at Yamuna Expressway, Greater Noida. At this carnival, the company has invited its customers and their families to enjoy the fun filled days. For kids, a special entertainment zone with games and rides has been made to engross them in different activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company is also giving special offers to the customers like assured gifts on every booking and on-the-spot home loan approvals.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/carniwal3.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/carniwal4.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n       <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/carniwal5.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/carniwal6.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n   \r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2013-01-12 00:00:00', 0),
(220, 'Supertech SERIES GOLF TOURNAMENTS', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech SERIES GOLF TOURNAMENTS</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[23&nbsp;December,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited is the main sponsor of Noida Golf Course series "which has three tournaments under his umbrella. "SUPERTECH SERIES OF DIWALI CUP" held in October 2014 "PRESIDENT CUP GOLF TOURNAMENT" held in November 2014 and now the "THE NEW YEAR CUP" which is going to happen on December 26 to 28, 2014, all at Noida Golf Course.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/supergolftour.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            \r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-12-23 00:00:00', 0),
(221, 'Supertech to Develop Affordable Housing Project "Basera" in Gurgaon', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech to Develop Affordable Housing Project "Basera" in Gurgaon</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[21&nbsp;November,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Gurgaon, November 21st, 2014: Gurgaon is touted to be one of the costliest residential destinations in Delhi NCR. With a vision of Government of India "Housing for All 2022", Supertech Limited is coming up with an affordable housing project "Basera" with a price range between Rs 12 lacs to 20 lacs. The project will be located in Sector 79 and Sector 79B of Gurgaon Manesar Urban Complex region.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The proposed project will be developed as per the terms and conditions of the policy prescribed by the Town & Country Planning Department, Government of Haryana. Applications are to be invited from general public for booking of Residential Apartments in this Affordable Housing Project. The allotment of apartments shall be done through the procedure of draw for lots.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Basera will spread over a sprawling area of 12.10 acres of land comprising a total 1976 flats, out of which 5% flats will be reserved for management quota and rest 95% is open for public.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. R. K Arora Chairman, Supertech Limited said, "Following the Government of India vision "Housing for All by 2022", this project will be Supertech''s first initiative under the policy of Haryana Government vide notification no PF-27/48921 dated 19.08.2013, We are very optimistic and looking forward to develop this project in Millennium city Gurgaon. The project would specially help the first-time homebuyers, who are struggling to buy a property due to current price escalations".</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The project will be constructed in two categories respectively 112 Flats of 404 sq.ft. (approx) carpet area with a two wheeler parking and 1744 flats of 546 Sq.ft. (approx) carpet area with a two-wheeler parking and 120 Flats of 592 Sq.ft. (approx) carpet area with a two-wheeler parking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The flat will be available with a cost ranging between Rs. 12,87,000 to Rs. 20,28,500 per flat depending upon the category allotted.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Highlights of Basera</p>\r\n<p>1. No maintenance charges for 5 years</p>\r\n<p>2. No escalation charges</p>\r\n<p>3. Guaranteed possession in 4 years</p>\r\n<p>4. Payment in installment</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/basera-img.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            \r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-11-21 00:00:00', 0),
(222, 'Supertech Sponsored "Run For Unity" in Greater Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Sponsored "Run For Unity" in Greater Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[31&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>To commemorate the birth anniversary of Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel, our Nation observers 31st October as Rashtriya Ekta Diwas every year. On this day, today, Supertech Limited was a part of Ã¢â‚¬Å“Run For UnityÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ marathon which was held in Greater Noida.</p>\r\n\r\n <p>The run saw the presence of around 500 people aged between 13 to 65 years who ran the 4 km route from City Park to Pari Chowk. Mr. P.K. Goel, Director, Supertech Limited flagged off the run for cause. The run started with singing of National Anthem at 6:00a.m. and went off till 8:00a.m. </p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/mr311.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/mr312.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/mr313.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            \r\n        </tr>\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-10-31 00:00:00', 0),
(223, 'Supertech Offered Possession of Capetown in Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Offered Possession of Capetown in Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[21&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited handed over the first phase Capetown project at Sector 74, Noida to the customers at a gala evening on Monday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company had invited its valued customers and their families to celebrate the possession ceremony of Capetown. At the ceremony, the key officials of the company, Mr. RK Arora, CMD, Supertech and Mr. G.L. Khera, Director, Supertech, addressed the customers and announced the possession of units and welcomed them to stay in their dream home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delighted at the ceremony, Mr. RK Arora, Chairman & Managing Director, Supertech Limited said, Ã¢â‚¬Å“It is indeed a very happy and proud moment for us while we offer possession of the first phase development of Capetown project to our customers. We are keeping our promise that we made to our customers with the timely possession of the project.Ã¢â‚¬Â</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To entertain the customers, the company had organized a live band which sung the popular foot tapping Bollywood numbers. Also, the customers relished the mouth watering snacks and dinner.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ctpc4.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ctpc3.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ctpc1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/ctpc2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-10-21 00:00:00', 0),
(224, 'Supertech Offered Possession of Eco Citi in Noida', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Offered Possession of Eco Citi in Noida</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[17&nbsp;October,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited handed over the first phase Eco Citi project at Sector 137, Noida-Greater Noida Expressway to the customers at a gala evening on Friday. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company had invited its valued customers and their families to celebrate the possession ceremony of Ecociti. At the ceremony, the key officials of the company, Mr. RK Arora, CMD, Supertech and Mr. G.L. Khera, Director, Supertech, addressed the customers and announced the possession of units and welcomed them to stay in their dream home. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delighted at the ceremony, Mr. RK Arora, Chairman & Managing Director, Supertech Limited said, Ã¢â‚¬Å“It is indeed a very happy and proud moment for us while we offer possession of the first phase development of Ecociti project to our customers. Ecociti is IndiaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s first Gold Standard approved residential development which sets apart the international standards. We are keeping our promise that we made to our customers with the timely possession of the project.Ã¢â‚¬Â</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To entertain the customers, the company had organized a live band which sung the popular foot tapping Bollywood numbers. Also, the customers relished the mouth watering snacks and dinner. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/evpc8.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n       