(229, 'Supertech proudly announces the launch of its first office in Lucknow (UP).', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech proudly announces the launch of its first office in Lucknow (UP).</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[4&nbsp;September,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/lo1.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/lo.jpg" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-09-04 00:00:00', 0),
(230, 'Supertech Limited Organized Bhoomi Pujan Of Hues', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited Organized Bhoomi Pujan Of Hues</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[9&nbsp;August,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Gurgaon, August 9, 2014: Supertech Limited, IndiaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s leading real estate developer, conducted the Bhoomi Pujan ceremony of Hues - Premium living in Sector 68, Gurgaon. The ceremony marked the commencement of construction of SupertechÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s second project in Gurgaon.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>The havan at the bhoomi pujan ceremony was performed by Mr. RK Arora, Chairman & Managing Director and other key officials of the company in the presence of around 500 customers.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>On the puja ceremony, Chairman & Managing Director of Supertech Limited, Mr. R.K Arora said, Ã¢â‚¬Å“Hues is our second project in Gurgaon which was launched 2 months back. The project has received an overwhelming response from the buyers in and around Gurgaon. We are very thankful to our valued customers for showing their trust in usÃ¢â‚¬Â.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Ã¢â‚¬Å“This premium residential development in Gurgaon will offer a serene lifestyle and will bring good investment opportunity for its prospective buyers. Due to its prime location, the project will be a perfect bliss for the people of GurgaonÃ¢â‚¬Â, added Mr. Arora. </p>\r\n \r\n<p>Hues is an integrated development comprises of 2 BHK, 2BHK+1study and 3 BHK units apartments. Marvelously designed ultra spacious apartments will have magnificent interiors with ultra rich furnishings and classy dÃƒÂ©cor. The project will have 2 level parking basement, double height entrance lobbies, around 85% green landscaped area, kids club house, jogging track, health centre, hi-end security, primary school, nursery school and a shopping centre. 20% of the project land has been exclusively reserved for facilities like schools, hospitals, parks, etc., which has been done for the first time in Gurgaon. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hues is ideally located at the intersection of Golf Course Extension Road and Sohna Road which is linked to major corporate hubs, retail destinations and Metro station. The project is in close proximity to major hospitals like Medicity and Artemis, world class educational institutions like Pathways and Goenka and is just a 30 minute drive from IGI Airport. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-08-09 00:00:00', 0);
