(231, 'Supertech Partners With The Xander Group', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Partners With The Xander Group</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[6&nbsp;August,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Global investment firm invests Rs. 400 crores in SupertechÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Gurgaon\r\nTownship & Group Housing Projects</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech Limited has received an investment of Rs. 400 crores (US$ 66 Million) from the Singapore based real estate investment arm of The Xander Group Inc. The investment has been made in SupertechÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Township and Group Housing projects in Sector 79, Gurgaon one of the fastest growing sectorÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s south of the NH-8.The GroupÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s project Ã¢â‚¬ËœAravilleÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ received an overwhelming response atlaunch, and the township is expected to perform on similar lines with redefined standards of urban living.  This investment and partnership with Xander strengthens the growth momentum of the Supertech Group.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Commenting on the transaction, Mr. R K Arora, CMD, Supertech Ltd, said Ã¢â‚¬Å“this single largest transaction in North India shows investorsÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ confidence in the capabilities of the Supertech Group. We are elated to join hands with Xander and look forward to have multiple investments from them in our Group.  Their persuasive industry knowledge and global experience will add cogent value to us.  Our transparency and fair practices have ensured that investors and buyers are happy to be associated with various projects of the Group.Ã¢â‚¬Â</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Rohan Sikri, Partner atXander Investment Management, Singapore said Ã¢â‚¬Å“we are pleased to partner with Supertech in these Gurgaon projects. As an experienced developer with a strong delivery track record, they have consistently shown commitment to execution and innovation. We continue to see the National Capital Region as an important market for us in India, and the relationship with Supertech, one of the largest NCR based developers, reinforces our investment appetite for end user focused residential projects with quality partners. Ã¢â‚¬Â </p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-08-06 00:00:00', 0),
(232, 'Supertech Felicitated by Hon''ble Union Minister Nitin Gadkari', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Felicitated by Hon''ble Union Minister Nitin Gadkari</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[22&nbsp;July,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p><b>Best Innovation In Real Estate Industry for Supernova </p></b>\r\n<p>Supertech Limited on July 21 evening received an award at a gala event, "Infra & Realty Sutra", organized by Gill India Concepts Pvt. Ltd at Shah Jehan Hall, Taj Palace, New Delhi. The Award Nite was held for the first time to recognize and applaud excellence in Indian Infrastructure and Real Estate and to set the most credible benchmark for the industry. The evening saw the presence of top personalities from infrastructure and real estate sectors from across the country.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Mr. Nitin Gadkari, Hon''ble Union Minister of Road Transport, Highways and Shipping, Chief Guest of the function gave away the awards. </p>\r\n\r\n <p>There were various categories to judge the parameters and to choose the best amongst it. For its unique innovative project Supernova-India''s largest mixed land use development, Supertech received an award under the "Best Innovation In Real Estate" category. Mr. R.K. Arora, Chairman & Managing Director and Mr. Mohit Arora, Director of Supertech Limited received the award.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/awa1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/awa2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/awa3.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/awa4.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/awa5.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            \r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-07-22 00:00:00', 0),
(233, 'Supertech Limited conducted the Bhoomi Pujan ceremony of Doon Square - company''s first project in Dehradun', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited conducted the Bhoomi Pujan ceremony of Doon Square - company''s first project in Dehradun</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[14&nbsp;July,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited conducted the Bhoomi Pujan ceremony of Doon Square Ã¢â‚¬â€œ company''s first project in Dehradun. The ceremony marked the commencement of construction of the premium commercial project in the city.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Doon Square is situated in the state Ã¢â‚¬â€œof-the-art SIDCUL IT Park at Sahastradhara Road, Dehradun.It has well developed residential sectors in the vicinity, and the thriving commercial & IT hub. This five storeyed project will accommodate Mall, Multiplex, Retail,office space, Serviced apartments and Hotel. The project is poised to be the hottest commercial destination in DehradunÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s economic future.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>The havan at the bhoomi pujan ceremony was performed by Mr. RK Arora, Chairman & Managing Director and other key officials of the company in the presence of around 300 customers.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>On the puja ceremony, Chairman & Managing Director of Supertech, Mr. R.K Arora said, "We are very delighted with our first prestigious project Doon Square, a premium commercial address in the developing region of SIDCUL. The project offers a serene lifestyle and brings good investment opportunity for its prospective buyers. Combining the elements of residential, retail, office and entertainment areas the project escalates as an ultimate destination for the people of Dehradun."</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Doon Square will be developed with well planned retail area, world class comfort and service , fully serviced studio apartments and also Hyphen Hotel that captures modern elegance in its most comfortable avatar.</p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-07-14 00:00:00', 0),
(234, 'Supertech Organized Property Carnival In association with HDFC Bank', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Organized Property Carnival In association with HDFC Bank</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[24&nbsp;May,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Rudrapur, 24th May 2014: Supertech Limited, has organized a three day property carnival in collaboration with HDFC Bank for its valued customers in the heart of city at Metropolis Mall in Rudrapur. The three day carnival spree started on May 24th and will end on May 26th.   </p>   \r\n\r\n<p>At the carnival, the city properties of Supertech were showcased and buyers and potential customers were invited to avail on-the-spot booking discounts being offered by Supertech. The company offered discounts on apartments, independent floors, villas, plots and suites at River Crest and Metropolis City. Working in tandem with a reputed bank gave a hassle free documentation process and zero processing fee on bookings made during the carnival. The company also offered special payment plans and facilitated housing loans in association with banks. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. R.K. Arora, Chairman & Managing Director, Supertech Limited said " Our main aim behind organizing such a carnival is that people of the city must get aware about the right kind of buying options available at right price in their vicinity and with such an easy and hassle free documentation at customers doorstep. We are getting full support and good queries from customers since the very first day of carnival and we hope to receive similar response from our elite customers".</p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-05-24 00:00:00', 0),
(235, 'Supertech Announced The Launch Of ''Hues'' - Premium Living In Sector 68, Gurgaon', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Announced The Launch Of ''Hues'' - Premium Living In Sector 68, Gurgaon</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[9&nbsp;May,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Gurgaon, May 9, 2014: Supertech Limited added another project in its portfolio of Gurgaon projects with the launch of ''Supertech Hues'' - Premium living in Sector 68, Gurgaon. The project is being developed by world renowned Singapore based architect Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Aedas and aims to provide an aesthetically pleasing and evolved lifestyle to the residences with excellence in architecture.</p>\r\n \r\n\r\n<p>First phase of Hues, which is a part of 70 acres of integrated development, is being launched with 23 towers and 2092 units offering options of 2 BHK, 2BHK+1study and 3 BHK units with area configuration ranging from 1180 sq. ft. to 1765 sq. ft., price starting from Rs. 84 lacs. Marvelously designed ultra spacious apartments will have magnificent interiors with ultra rich furnishings and classy dÃƒÂ©cor. The 3 side open apartments with huge balconies will provide a panoramic view, high ceilings which will give room for air and more space making the apartments look much bigger and better in every sense and modular styling to keep the kitchen hygienic.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech Hues will have 2 level parking basement, double height entrance lobbies, around 85% green landscaped area, kids club house, jogging track, health centre, hi-end security, primary school, nursery school and a shopping centre. 20% of the project land has been exclusively reserved for facilities like schools, hospitals, parks, etc., which has been done for the first time in Gurgaon. </p>\r\n<p>The total investment on the first phase of the project would be around Rs. 1,000 crores.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Speaking on the occasion, Mr. R K Arora, Chairman & Managing Director, Supertech Limited said, "Hues is our second project in the millennium city, Gurgaon. Our first project Araville got overwhelming response from the buyers and we are sure that Hues would receive the same. Keeping in mind the lifestyle demands and aspirations of the corporate segment working in Gurgaon, we launched this luxurious project which is strategically located in the new sector of Gurgaon-one of the hottest realty markets of the region. The project enjoys great location advantage being in close proximity of schools, hospitals and major conveniences and is an integrated part of a fully developed infrastructure".</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>"The beautifully designed apartments with breathtaking interiors and spectacular designs will surely take the residents to a new address of living", added Mr. Arora.</p>\r\n \r\n\r\n<p>Hues is ideally located at the intersection of Golf Course Extension Road and Sohna Road which is linked to major corporate hubs, retail destinations and Metro station. The project is in close proximity to major hospitals like Medicity and Artemis, world class educational institutions like Pathways and Goenka and is just a 30 minute drive from IGI Airport.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/hues1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/hues2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-05-09 00:00:00', 0),
(236, 'Supertech Limited Orgainsed A Fun-filled Weekend For Its Customers At Upcountry, Yamuna Expressway', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Limited Orgainsed A Fun-filled Weekend For Its Customers At Upcountry, Yamuna Expressway</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[30&nbsp;March,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited orgainsed an eventful weekend on March 29 and 30 at its Upcountry project at Yamuna Expressway. The company had invited people from all across the city to enjoy action-packed carnival, Ã¢â‚¬ËœRace OnÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ which had activities such as Go-Karting, Cycling and Segway Rides. The event also had scrumptious food and an entertainment zone for kids.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>The event witnessed a huge crowd gathering which was enticed towards activities of Go-karting and Segway.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>The gala event was held at companyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s 100 township project, Upcounty located at Yamuna Expressway which gave a feeling of country-side to the visitors. It was a great opportunity for the company to showcase its huge township and its unique features like man-made beaches and ultra luxurious high end villas. The project also has high rise condominiums, plots, studio apartments, school, medical centres, club houses and a shopping mall.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/gok1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/gok2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/gok3.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/gok4.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/gok5.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/gok6.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-03-30 00:00:00', 0),
(237, 'Supertech bags Top Residential Space Developer-NCR', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech bags Top Residential Space Developer-NCR</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[24&nbsp;March,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech limited wins Ã¢â‚¬ËœTop Residential Space Developer Ã¢â‚¬â€œ NCRÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ from Mail Today Group. CMD Mr.R.K.Arora and Director Mr. Mohit Arora jointly received the award from Mr. Rama Raman, Chairman and CEO, Noida Authority. On this occasion, Mr. Ajay Maken, General Secretary Congress, Mr. Abhishek Mishra, UP Science and Technology Minister and some prominent Developers of Delhi NCR were also present. It is one of the prestigious Realty sector Award in Delhi NCR.</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            \r\n            <td align="center">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/mailtodayaward.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-03-24 00:00:00', 0),
(238, 'Supertech Entered Into Bengaluru With ''Micasa''', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Entered Into Bengaluru With ''Micasa''</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[1&nbsp;February,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>Supertech Limited, a reputed and known name in North India''s real estate industry has now entered the Southern part of India with its first project, Micasa in Bengaluru. Supertech announced its first residential project in the city which will have ''Spanish Styled apartments'' at Thanisandra Road in North Bengaluru.</p>\r\n \r\n <p>Micasa will provide aesthetically designed apartments in 2 & 3 BHK options. The area of these units will range between 1100 sq. ft. to 1735 sq. ft. These lavishly furnished apartments are planned according to the Spanish grandeur which is spread all across the township. This spectacular project will offer around 200 residential units within the price range of Rs. 3790 per sq. ft in phase 1 which is going to increase up 1000 unit in phase 2.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Speaking on the occasion of launch of Micasa, Mr. Mohit Arora, Director, Supertech Limited said, "We are thrilled to have our first venture in Bengaluru with Supertech Micasa with its innovative features and unbeatable location. The IT hub a stoneÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s throw away, virtually assures capital appreciation. With vibrant Spanish architectural designs, Micasa will be an epitome of opulence, luxury and elegance, with the world class luxurious modern conveniences."</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Micasa is a Spanish word that means ''My Home'' in English and is the first project of Supertech Ltd in Bengaluru city. Bengaluru being a topper of the list of major Indian cities and is one of the most popular real estate destinations in Southern India, is one major reason that the group chose the city for launching this project. Spread across 76,230 sq ft of land parcel, Supertech Micasa is inspired from ''Spanish architectural style'' and is offering opulent 2/3 BHK apartments. Located on Thanisandra Road, North Bengaluru. The entire project once completed will offer some of the best in class amenities and facilities to its residents. In short the residents at Supertech Micasa can enjoy blissful living that will come equipped with international style features with a hint of Spanish flavor further added by Mohit.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Located at a posh locality of the ''Silicon Valley'', these exceptional homes are discerningly carved out to offer a niche lifestyle to its residents with international standard and a Spanish tint. The Thanisandra Road region where Supertech Micasa will be located remains to be a serene situated area, with all prime locations connected to it and all major facilities located in its neighboring locale. The region has got enormous potential and the city has also seen a great raise in immigration of professional from other cities, thus creating a huge gap in demand and supply for luxury houses.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Supertech Micasa will be situated near Yelahanka which is regarded as one of the most premium location in Bengaluru due to the Kempegowda International airport. Moreover, the 6-lane signal-less road linking the main business region to Manchester International has also proved helpful in support of the project.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Artistically designed, the project will be well equipped with all the necessary and high tech facilities which a modern home demands. The amenities will include a swimming pool, clubhouses, gymnasiums, pool tables, table tennis arenas, etc. Apart from this, the campus of the project will have clean green- manicured lawns, kidsÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ play area, reserved parking spaces, Wi-Fi connectivity in campus, CCTV Surveillance cameras, fire safety measures etc. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/micasa1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/micasa2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/micasa3.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/micasa4.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-02-01 00:00:00', 0),
(239, 'Supertech Ventured Into Higher Education With The Launch Of Supertech University', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Ventured Into Higher Education With The Launch Of Supertech University</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[23&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><P>Supertech Ventured Into Higher Education With The Launch Of Supertech University</p>\r\n \r\n<P>Supertech is diversifying into Education, marked by the announcement to launch Supertech University, an initiative of Supertech Foundation, which is being set up in Udham Singh Nagar district of Uttarakhand.</p>\r\n \r\n<P>Located at the foothills of Himalayas in Uttarakhand, on a land of 47 acre lush green campus, approximately 237 Km from Delhi, this university will be the first major milestone by Supertech into the higher education sector. Supertech University aims at creating a value-based, innovation driven, and research led world-class teaching and learning environment. The University will offer programmes in the domains of Architecture and Planning, Earth, Environment and Space Studies, Education, Engineering and Technology, Fashion and Design, Hospitality and Tourism, Languages and Communication, Law and Governance, Liberal Arts, Humanities and Social Sciences, Management Studies, Medical and Health Sciences, Natural and Applied Sciences and Public Policy.</p>\r\n \r\n<P>Delighted at this new venture, Mr. R K Arora, Chairman & Managing Director, Supertech Limited said, "Supertech University will be our first venture in the education sector. Building homes to building institutions is a leap of faith inspired by motivation to touch lives of millions, bringing about transformative changes. I sincerely believe that when the student is ready, the teacher appears. Therefore, it is my proud privilege to announce for those aspiring students of the country who felt the need for a world class institution matching their ambition, here is an opportunity to give flight to their imagination and take off. Supertech with its brand value will provide the requisite wherewithal towards its fruition and growth".    </p>\r\n \r\n<P>Speaking on the occasion, Prof. V P S Arora, Vice Chancellor, Supertech University said, "I am immensely happy and feel honored to be part of this University from the inception and nurture it into an island of excellence as its Founding Vice Chancellor. I congratulate Mr. R K Arora and his dedicated team for showing their deep commitment towards education which is a game changer. Only a visionary will think of enduring value creation. Coming in the aftermath of one of the biggest humanitarian tragedies in Uttarakhand, such altruism couldnÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t be more appropriate and timely".</p>\r\n \r\n<P>Differentiators of Supertech University from its peers are:</p>\r\n\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·                Rich Intellectual Capital in the form of committed patronage, mentoring, and guidance by former and sitting Vice Chancellors, Corporate Leaders, Scientists, Reformers, and former Ambassador</p>\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·                 Balanced focus on Capacity Building, Consulting, Education,  Innovation, Research, and Skill Development activities</p>\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·            A wide array of programmes to choose from including flagship programmes like Public Policy Studies and Infrastructure Management</p>\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·  Innovative Teaching Learning Pedagogic Approach including :</p>\r\n\r\n  <P>Flexible and non conventional course combinations</p>\r\n\r\n<P>  Concept of basket courses</p>\r\n\r\n<P>  Choice based credit system</p>\r\n\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·                     Strong Corporate Brand behind the University</p>\r\n\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·                  Creation of Directorate of Skill Development to enhance the employability quotient of youth and contribute to this gigantic skill deficit in the country</p>\r\n\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·              Values, Culture and Ethics based education by introducing the study of behavioural science and ethics compulsory</p>\r\n\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·                    Tie up with reputed national and international academic institutions</p>\r\n\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·                     State of Art Infrastructure Facilities</p>\r\n<P>Ã‚Â·                     Fully Residential and Green Campus, ensuring productive and healthy campus life to students and staff</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/su1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/su2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-01-23 00:00:00', 0),
(240, 'Supertech Announced The Launch Of ''The Romano''', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">Supertech Announced The Launch Of ''The Romano''</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[20&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><h3>Roman Styled Luxurious Apartments in the heart of Noida</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech Limited after successfully delivering many magnificent projects in Noida announced the launch of another residential project ''The Romano'' Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Roman Style living in Sector 118, Noida on January 20, ''14. The project will be a perfect melange of ancient glory and contemporary luxury.</p>\r\n \r\n<p>Spread over area of 17.5 acres, The Romano comprises of 18 towers with 1800 fully finished luxurious apartments in 2, and 3 BHK options set amidst internationally designed landscape. The area of these units will range from 1,020 sq. ft to 2,170 sq. ft., priced at Rs. 4,350 per sq. ft. The project has a unique feature of Roman styled architecture which will provide an aesthetically pleasing and evolved lifestyle to the residences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the announcement of the project, Mr. R. K. Arora, Chairman & Managing Director, Supertech Ltd opined, "The launch of The Romano marks the commitment of Supertech to continuously develop properties with modern and high tech facilities which redefines the experience of living in a modern aesthetic way. The Romano will further bring fully finished luxurious apartments to our customers. We pride ourselves on exceptional customer service and providing an extraordinary lifestyle for our residents."</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Strategically located on FNG expressway, this river facing development enjoys enviable connectivity through a network of roads, national highways and flyovers. Due to its easy accessibility from the capital and other suburbs, encompassed by the Metro Station, it offers a great residential solution to the working people. The project is well equipped with all the necessary and high tech facilities which a modern home demands. Some of the feature includes Club House, Gymnasium, modular kitchen, hospital, bank, crÃƒÂ¨che, playground, CCTV Cameras, shopping centres.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Romano is all set to add  another prospect in the company''s asset, which already has projects like Supernova which is India''s tallest & biggest mixed - use development and North Eye, North India''s tallest & luxurious residential project , in its itinerary .</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="720" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp</td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n			&nbsp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n       \r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n			<img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/rom1.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n            <td align="right">\r\n            <img border="0" src="http://www.supertechlimited.com/images/rom2.JPG" alt="" /></td>\r\n			</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-01-20 00:00:00', 0),
(241, 'International Designer ''yoo'' Forays Into Gurgaon With Supertech', '<div class="bodytext">\r\n			 <p style="float:right;"><a href="media-news.asp?nYear=2014&mon=" class="back">Back</a></p>\r\n				          <div class="mediaprtitle">International Designer ''yoo'' Forays Into Gurgaon With Supertech</div>\r\n				          <p style="font-size:12px!important;">[15&nbsp;January,&nbsp;2014]</p>\r\n				          <p><p>New Delhi, January 15, 2014:  yoo Worldwide LLP, the global design, development and branding firm, is to create two luxurious residential projects in Gurgaon''s premium Sector 68 and 79. yoo will work with Supertech Limited to produce one residential project with the Jade Jagger for yoo property brand and a separate residential project with Steve Leung & yoo, another of yooÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s successful property brands. yoo will deliver unique design concepts to each project that will reflect the kind of innovative, international design style that is synonymous with the firm.  </p>\r\n\r\n <p>The projects will benefit from either Jade Jagger or Steve Leung''s distinctive styles, both of which are available in Gurgaon for the first time. Jade''s style is characterised by her use of colour and for creating spaces which allow families to relax and enjoy one anotherÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s company. Jade is known for works including The Jade in New York City. Steve Leung is lauded as one of the world''s leading architects and designers, whose work is known for its minimal and eastern influence Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Steve Leung was responsible for the successful ''yoo Residence'' in Hong Kong and the upcoming Shangri-La London Hotel in The Shard.</p>\r\n\r\n <p>Mr. R.K. Arora, CMD, Supertech Limited said: "yoo is a luxury brand which provides exclusive interior design solutions for high-end properties. Our association with yoo will provide unrivalled luxury and an unforgettable living experience for our customers. The skill and expertise of Jade Jagger and Steve Leung will create a beyond luxury concept in India."</p>\r\n\r\n <p>John Hitchcox, Chairman of yoo, comments: "yoo is excited to work with Supertech, India''s leading real estate developer on this unique project. Jade has a special relationship with India and the country''s culture and style having lived here for over 20 years. She and Steve are two of the very best designers and will create two beautiful residences in this buzzing city."  </p></p>\r\n										<p>\r\n                      </p>\r\n					\r\n				          \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			          </div>', 0, 1, '2014-01-15 00:00:00', 0),
