(46, NULL, 'Fable Castle', 29, 'Welcome to Fable Castle', NULL, 'Greater Noida', '26284', 'Early 2018', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<div class="subtitle">Where there is a story at every step</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Think of Wishing Wells granting you your every wish. Envisage elegant Princesses grace your garden through winter,spring and summer.Visualize your favourite characters bringing back magic to everyday living. It&#39;s about to come to life with a whole new world; complete with picturesque castles, your favorite characters and breathtaking activities that mesmerized you as a child. Ever wish to turn back the calender and live your childhood again? Come over; experience a spellbinding story waiting for you every moment and every step along the way.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Where the World of fantasy is a part of your World</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to a destination where every creation is as vivid as your imagination. Fable Castle is a place for the young and old, big and small - a unique space where great moments cone to life as you relive your childhood, all over again! Discover a fabulous and enchanting world inspired by the stories, characters and the magic of fantasy. Create precious memories with your family that will last a lifetime as you discover a new and magical lifestyle. The 2/3/4 BHK apartments at Fable Castle will take you to a world where fables come to life, immersing you in lifestyle inspired by some of your favourite fantasy stories and films. The World of fantasy can be part of your world now.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Where everyday life boasts a fairytale delights</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Enter this wonderful fabled world where you can live in a world inspired with the characters from your favorite fantasy stories. Encounter Princess from the Royal Realms of fantasy. Follow Snow White into the woods. Admire Sleeping Beauty in deep slumber. Watch ride away in her pumpkin carriage to meet her Prince charming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Live a fairy tale everyday with magical characters as you engage in the magic of fantasy story telling. Party with family and friends at a fantasy themed club house. Have fun n&#39; frolic in the heartshaped pools. Take a stroll in he garden inspired by natures. Drop a coin in the Wishing Well to make every wish come true.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Where the living space speaks of your favourite fantasy characters</div>\r\n\r\n<p>At Fable Castle your rooms can be customised with your child&#39;s favourite fantasy characters. Let them enjoy a new experience inspired by fantasy, while you re-live the joys of your favourite fantasy stories. Whatever your child&#39;s age may be, there is magic for everyone.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 'logo_1439290214.png', 'fable_pic_1439290214.jpg', NULL, 'siteplan_1439290214.jpg', '3150000', '0', '2015-08-11 16:20:14', '2015-09-09 19:10:15', 1, 0, 0, '', '2, 3 & 4 BHK', 2, '2018-01-01'),
(47, NULL, 'Meerut Sports City', 43, 'Welcome to Meerut Sports City', NULL, 'Greater Noida', '11451', 'Late 2014', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>A unique design approach unifying modern architecture with sports facilities</li>\r\n	<li>Close to the hustle bustle of Meerut</li>\r\n	<li>Designed for healthy and balanced lifestyle in a green sanctuary</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to Meerut Sports City !</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Put on your sports attire, let your hair down &amp; let the surroundings take over.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Close to the hustle bustle of Meerut yet in the lap of nature lies a delightful hidden gateway designed for healthy and balanced lifestyle in a green sanctuary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A unique design approach unifying modern architecture with sports facilities will include beautifully designed high-rise tower &amp; superb villas along with a full size cricket stadium, boating lake and putting greens.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Meerut Sports City, A Metropolitan City.</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Meerut Sports City, a modern world spread across 51 acres of prime land, is all set to introduce you to the metropolitan lifestyle. Clubbing together matchless luxuries of modern lifestyle and architectural brilliance of international standards, this integrated township will offer you a lifestyle beyond imagination, right here in Meerut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Come, discover the joy of healthy &amp; playful living.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_meerutsports_1439294661.png', 'meerutsportcity-pic1_1439294661.jpg', NULL, 'siteplan_1439294661.jpg', '1372410', '0', '2015-08-11 17:34:21', '2015-09-21 15:55:48', 1, 0, 0, '', '1, 2, 3 & 4 BHK', 2, '2014-12-31'),
(48, NULL, 'Green Village', 43, 'Welcome to Green Village, Meerut', NULL, 'Meerut', '11473', 'Late 2014', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>Supertech Group has recently launched its new township, Supertech &quot;GREEN VILLAGE&quot; adjoining to its successful ongoing Group Housing project &quot;Palm Greens&quot; in Meerut. Meerut is rapidly growing and going to be one of the most sought after destinations. Further, with the completion of the proposed Expressway between Delhi and Meerut, properties of Meerut are bound to appreciate tremendously. Meerut has seen a boom in real estate business for the past decade and the city is now flush with new high rise shopping Complex, apartment building and businesses. Meerut is the largest manufacturer of musical instruments in India and is also one of the largest suppliers of export goods. Meerut is well known for its historical anecdotes and nowadays Meerut is emerging as an alternative of metros like Delhi and other adjoining cities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The basic concept behind Green Village project is to provide flats and apartments for middle income group people who cannot afford the burden of living in a metro but they have aspiration and dream to avail all the modern and comfortable amenities of metro city. Green Village consists of around 1200 units of high &amp; low rise apartments built with most modern amenities such as an international standard club with 7star facilities necessary for comfortable living, at very special and reasonable price. Green village is planned on 25 acres of land that contains 1, 2, 3 &amp; 4 BHK flats &amp; Independent Villas with exclusive design of every room opens in balcony and of course, in front of nature.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_1439297828.png', 'green_pic1_1439297828.jpg', NULL, 'siteplan_1439297828.jpg', '1375000', '0', '2015-08-11 18:27:08', '2015-09-21 15:56:00', 1, 0, 0, '', '1, 2, 3 & 4 BHK', 2, '2014-12-31'),
(49, NULL, 'Micasa', 44, 'BIENVENIDA a ''MI CASA''- Welcome to Micasa', NULL, 'Bangalore', '32133', 'August 2016', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>For the Spanish, it&#39;s all about passion and enjoying every moment as it comes. Inspired by their liveliness and spontaneity, we have developed a unique Lifestyle project... that truly exudes the magnificent culture of Spain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Spaniards very often say &#39;Mi Casa... Su Casa&#39;, which literally means &#39;Consider my home as your home&#39;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And to make these homes just as welcoming, we have paid attention to every minute detail... beginning right from the vibrant Spanish architectural designing style. The project is designed keeping a keen eye on all the luxury and lifestyle needs that you can ever expect from your Casa. A variety of lavish and &#39;thought-after&#39; amenities are added just to make your life more pleasurable, peaceful, entertaining and lively. Or as the Spanish say... Fantastico!</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle" style="margin-top:0px;">Bien Ubicado &ndash; Well Located</div>\r\n\r\n<p>When you live at Micasa; you are not far from anywhere!</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>10 Mins. drive to Kogilu Junction</li>\r\n	<li>20 Mins. drive to Bangalore International Airport</li>\r\n	<li>25 Mins. drive to Hebbal Flyover</li>\r\n	<li>30 Mins. drive to MG Road</li>\r\n	<li>35 Mins. drive to KR Puram</li>\r\n	<li>40 Mins. drive to Whitefield</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Conseguir Encantado &ndash; Get Enchanted</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>Swimming Pool</li>\r\n	<li>Table Tennis Room</li>\r\n	<li>Central Landscaped Park</li>\r\n	<li>Children&#39;s Play Area</li>\r\n	<li>Open &amp; Closed Parking</li>\r\n	<li>CCTV Covered Property</li>\r\n	<li>Paved Surfaces</li>\r\n	<li>Fire Safety</li>\r\n	<li>Club House with Pool Table and other Indoor Games</li>\r\n	<li>Fully &ndash; Equipped Gymnasium</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_micasa_1439356694.png', 'micasa-pic1_1439356746.jpg', NULL, NULL, '4994000', '0', '2015-08-12 10:48:14', '2015-09-09 17:08:59', 1, 5, 0, '', '2 & 3 BHK', 2, '2016-08-31'),
(50, NULL, 'River Crest', 45, 'Welcome to River Crest, Rudrapur', NULL, 'Pant Nagar Uttarakhand', '14171', '-', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>Rudrapur is a growing city in several ways. Many multi-national brands vouch for the place and plan to expand furthermore. The residential sector is also blooming with world-class developments like Supertech RiverCrest, a 24 acre metropolitan township. Come, enjoy riverside living and be surrounded by scenic beauty.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_1439359690.png', 'rivercrest_pic1_1439359690.jpg', NULL, 'siteplan_1439359690.jpg', '1659120', '0', '2015-08-12 11:38:10', '2015-09-10 10:15:37', 1, 0, 0, '', '2 BHK', 3, '0000-00-00'),
(51, NULL, 'Livingston', 46, 'Welcome to Livingston, Ghaziabad', NULL, 'Ghaziabad', '24137', 'Late 2014', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>Supertech Livingston is set amidst beautiful lush greens to make you feel rejuvenated. This spectacular township is located in the heart of the country and offers 70% of open area within each plot. The open spaces at Livingston enthrall not just your mind, but also your spirit. The spaces have been designed keeping in mind your need for expansive spaces that capture your imagination. The township is a synonym for clutter free, pollution free, rejuvenating atmosphere that fosters harmonious co-existence with natural surroundings. Replete with facilities such as school, shopping mall, golf course etc, it is built with a view to provide you world-class amenities within close vicinity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Livingston is being developed within the premises of India&#39;s first global city - Crossings Republik in Ghaziabad. This project is an amalgamation of 7 real estate companies including Supertech Group. All companies conceived together a global city which is culminated in the form Crossings Repulik and within this global city Livingston is being developed by Supertech Group. Project location of Livingston which falls under territory of Ghaziabad is rapidly growing and featured in Newsweek International as the 10 top most dynamic cities of the world during the year 2006. It is on its way to becoming one of the most advanced and top class cities in the world and stands as the perfect investment and housing destination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Livingston is a part of integrated township spread across 360 acres. It is committed to provide you a luxurious lifestyle in your dream home within this township. Replete with all facilities one can possibly think of, such as ultra modern apartments, golf course, clubs, swimming pool, shopping malls, daily needs stores, hospitals and a gymnasium. You shall be greeted with an absolutely blissful environment devoid of chaos and pollution, where lush greens and wide open spaces await you. You feel like you are in a world so different and pure. Located within close vicinity to Noida, Greater Noida, New Delhi, Airport, Railway Station a developing Metro line, this is the place you want to spend the life that you deserve.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_1439362137.png', 'livingston-pic1_1439362137.jpg', NULL, 'siteplan_1439362137.jpg', '2892750', '0', '2015-08-12 12:18:57', '2015-09-10 10:17:02', 1, 0, 0, '', '2 & 3 BHK', 2, '2014-12-31'),
(52, NULL, 'Palm Greens', 47, 'Welcome to Palm Greens, Moradabad', NULL, 'Moradabad', '20902', 'January 2007', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>Supertech Palm Greens Moradabad is set amidst beautiful lush greens to make you feel rejuvenated. Supertech Palm Greens provides you 70% of the open area and an option of 2, 3 &amp; 4 Bed rooms premium apartments. A 5 star Hotel is located adjacent to project site which is on National Highway - 24 (Delhi - Hapur - Gajraula - Moradabad), approx 150 KM from NCR Delhi. Besides that Palm Greens is well connected by railway, nearest railway station is just 13 KM away, and by a proposed Airport (Mundapande) is just 20 KM away. Your stay in Palm Greens, Moradabad, is surely going to be spiced up. So be ready to experience a world-class infrastructure in Supertech Palm Green Moradabad with its screen surroundings and an ultra modern life style all within your reach in a pollution free environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech is committed to provide world class living ambience not only at Metros and Big Cities but also in comparatively small but rapidly emerging cities like Moradabad in Uttar Pradesh. Our one of the flagship project is taking shape right here as in form of Palm Greens, Moradabad. In Palm Greens project, Supertech is providing premium apartments with all infrastructure and luxuries of Metro away from actual metro city. Palm Greens is concept of residential project in the lap of nature and ecology with the ample open green space. Supertech has constantly strived to offer you true-value for money homes that are the best in quality construction and finest facilities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_1439364786.png', 'palmgreens_pic1_1439364786.jpg', NULL, 'siteplan_1439364786.jpg', '2505000', '0', '2015-08-12 13:03:06', '2015-09-10 10:18:19', 1, 0, 0, '', '2, 3 & 4 BHK', 2, '2017-01-31'),
(53, NULL, 'Doon Square', 48, 'Welcome to Doon Square, Dehradun', NULL, 'Dehradun', '0', 'Not Available', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>Dehradun is located just 230 kilometers from the national capital and is well connected by road, rail and air to major Indian cities. Its proximity to the sacred Ganga river, the religious towns of Rishikesh, Haridwar, Badrinath and Kedarnath and the popular hill station of Mussourie makes it an important destination for tourists and adventure sports lovers. Dehradun property has seen a major boom since its instatement as the capital. People from all over the country including NRIs (Non Resident Indians) have been aggressively investing in the city. According to the survey conducted by Business Standard, Dehradun ranks 5th on NRIs list of property investment destination. Properties in Dehradun promise you a high return on investment both financially and by quality of life. Uttarakhand government has taken active steps in improving the infrastructure of the city.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today Dehradun can boast of having one of the best power and water supply distribution schemes in the entire country.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Doon Square.<br />\r\nThe hottest destination in Dehradun&#39;s economic future.</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Supertech presents Doon Square; the commercial project that&#39;s already the talk of Dehradun town. Situated at the epicenter of SIDCUL IT Park, Doon Square is poised to be the hottest commercial destination in Dehradun&#39;s economic future. Spread over 4.2 acres, this 5 - storey project accommodates mall, multiplex, retail, serviced suites and hotel. The project also offers great returns on investment. Doon Square is located in the heart of state-of-the-art SIDCUL Information Park in more than 60 acres at Sahastradhara road, Dehradun, the state capital with intelligent buildings and hi-tech habitat centre. The state government has undertaken major initiatives in IT Education, formulation of a Pro-active IT Policy and development of International Quality infrastructure.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_doonSquare_1439366354.png', 'doonsquare_1440591464.jpg', NULL, 'siteplan_1439366354.jpg', '0', '0', '2015-08-12 13:29:14', '2015-09-10 10:19:02', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 3, '0000-00-00'),
(54, NULL, 'E Square', 28, 'Welcome to E Square, Noida', NULL, 'Noida', '0', 'Mid 2016', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<div class="subtitlespecial">What&#39;s Special</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>A Supertech brand of high value.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">USPs</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>Unique Perspective: Glass view gives a bird&#39;s eye view of Noida Expressway on one side &amp; greens on the other.</li>\r\n	<li>Facing IT hub of Noida.</li>\r\n	<li>A mix of retail, commercial &amp; entertainment zone.</li>\r\n	<li>Four-side open plot ringed with ornamental trees.</li>\r\n	<li>Scalable Offices: Office spaces ranging from 520 to 15,000 sq.ft. in single floor plate.</li>\r\n	<li>High Visibility: Retail area visible from Expressway.</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent Ambience: Plot has unique location flanked on both sides by two hotel sites.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Addressable Market</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>More than 10,000 families ready to residing in vicinity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Cost Advantage</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>Low Maintenance cost.</li>\r\n	<li>24 X 7 power back up.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_esquare_1439371627.png', 'esquare-pic1_1439371627.jpg', NULL, NULL, '3744000', '0', '2015-08-12 14:57:07', '2015-09-10 10:20:01', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 2, '2016-06-30'),
(55, NULL, 'Oxford Square', 30, 'Welcome to Oxford Square, Greater Noida (West)', NULL, 'Greater Noida (West)', '37680', 'March 2015', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>Welcome to the world class, independent living spaces at Oxford Square, Greater Noida.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These Independent Floors provide a freedom of living where you are not forced to live in claustrophobic environment. Each of the independent floors is designed to give you a feel of life in a villa and a great sense of space. Independent Floors at Oxford Square is truly an address you have always aspired for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Life at Oxford Square is a perfect blend of open spaces, community living and conveniences. With exclusive features like a terrace garden, a splash pool and a lot more, life at Oxford Square is a perfect blend of open spaces, community living and conveniences. You will not be forced to share your world with anyone else. With state-of-the-art security, gated complex, wide internal roads, shopping complex, modern club, gym etc., you can now enjoy independent living on your very own floor.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_1441698231.png', 'oxfordsquare-pic1_1441698231.jpg', NULL, NULL, '4511276', '0', '2015-08-12 16:27:46', '2015-09-10 10:22:15', 1, 0, 0, '1,2 & 3 BHK', '1, 2 & 3 BHK', 2, '2015-03-31'),
