(58, NULL, 'Shopprix Mall', 43, 'Welcome to Shopprix Mall, Meerut', NULL, 'Meerut', '0', 'NA', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<div class="subtitlespecial">What&#39;s Special</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>Spread over 4,50,000 sq. ft., fully air-conditioned.</li>\r\n	<li>3-screen multiplex comprising of 30,000 sq. ft.</li>\r\n	<li>4-star hotel of 85 rooms and a banquet hall in the mall.</li>\r\n	<li>S-Shaped atrium, classic interiors, signage visibility and large-scale corridors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Meerut has been fast catching up with the developed areas in the vicinity and acquiring a new identity. Supertech&#39;s revolutionary move to establish an all-in-one mall in Meerut has provided a much-needed boost and opened the doors to a new era.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spread over 4,50,000 sq. ft., fully air-conditioned, with a 3-screen multiplex comprising of 30,000 sq. ft. and huge food court to cater all taste buds. Having top-of-the-line brands, Shopprix realizes the long-discussed novel idea of a Mall Hotel by having a 4 star hotel of 85 rooms and a banquet hall in the mall. Modern management services, power-back up, air conditioning, 1000 parking space and top-quality safety systems take it head and shoulders above any other mall in Meerut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is more is the unheard-of facility of conference rooms and business centre which provides the option of business and entertainment going hand-in-hand. Plus the Meerut Haat, Jewelry Mart, sports good shops and 20,000 sq. ft. of area reserved for kids zone, ensuring that there is something for everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The USP of Shopprix lies in its S-Shaped atrium, classic interiors, signage visibility and large-scale corridors which make every stall and shop stand out from the crowd and speak.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Truly a remarkable idea bringing Retail, Entertainment, Services and Hospitality Industry together to redefine the concept of a shopping mall.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_shopprix_1439535034.png', 'shopprixmall_1439535034.jpg', NULL, NULL, '900000', '0', '2015-08-14 12:20:34', '2015-09-09 14:59:15', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '0000-00-00'),
(59, NULL, 'The Pentagon Mall', 49, 'Operational from April 2012', NULL, 'Haridwar', '0', 'Operational', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<div class="subtitle">Whats Special</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>First and the biggest Mall cum Multiplex of entire Uttarakhand.</li>\r\n	<li>Located in the prime vicinity of SIDCUL compound in New Haridwar</li>\r\n	<li>Some of the biggest brands like Mc Donalds, Reliance Footprints, Bikanervala, DLF AVE.NUE, Wave Cinemas, Ritu Wears Big Life, Woodland, Spencers, Reliance Trends, Reliance Footprints etc. already put their trust on us.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Haridwar is one of the places where the drops of the elixir of immortality, Amrita, accidentally spilled from the pitcher of the celestial bird Garuda. Ever since it has become a religious destination for the Hindu. Situated in the banks of the holy Ganges, Haridwar has found its place in many Hindu scriptures. But this heritage and culture hasn&#39;t misplaced the idea of development and modernity. It is fast emerging as a business hub of Uttrakhand. Therefore, seeing the immense potential of Haridwar, Supertech has built the first of its kind mall - The Pentagon Mall here.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="subtitle">Opportunities Galore</div>\r\n\r\n<p>This is where tradition meets modernity. Inspired with this philosophy, The Pentagon Mall has brought world class business opportunities to Haridwar. Located in the prime vicinity of SIDCUL compound in New Haridwar, The Pentagon Mall is easily accessible. It offers around 7,50,000 Sq. Ft. of area in five floors, which are designed according to their utility without compromising on the aesthetics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An entertainment area dedicated only to kids, with gaming zones and other sporting arcades.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A huge food court with multi-cuisine outlets, a first-of-its-kind in Uttarakhand and fine dining restaurants catering to all tastes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hyper market of approximately catering to all the needs of a household like groceries, apparels, footwear, kitchenware, house furnishings, and many national and international products. First class experience of movie viewing would be a first time experience for Haridwar and surrounding areas.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_pentagon_1439538186.png', 'pentagon-pic1_1439538186.jpg', NULL, NULL, '800000', '0', '2015-08-14 13:13:06', '2015-09-09 14:35:09', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '0000-00-00'),
(60, NULL, 'Metropolis Mall, Rudrapur', 45, 'Welcome to Metropolis Mall, Rudrapur', NULL, 'Rudrapur Uttarakhand', '0', 'NA', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<ul class="ul-text">\r\n	<li>The Metropolis Mall is located on the main Delhi - Nainital National Highway 87. Strategic location just opposite to Ginger Hotel and DM office, SIDCUL, Rudrapur</li>\r\n	<li>3,00,000 Sqft of Retail development. Huge frontage of 400 ft. approx having main access from the highway.</li>\r\n	<li>Part of 55 acre Group housing development.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>With a vision to create residential, commercial and retail magic, two leading real estate companies, ASSOTECH &amp; SUPERTECH have collaborated their forces to bring - THE METROPOLIS MALL. Two leaders in the Indian real estate canvas, who have their architectural and building prowess across International and Indian domestic civil projects. Each, a demonstration of competence in the design and execution with a special accent on early delivery and completion. A trademark sign off that has thousands of clients in the commercial and housing sectors extremely happy and satisfied.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Metropolis Mall, Being built on land allotted and approved by SIDCUL, is all set to take Rudrapur by storm. This project is less than 100 metres away from the Mega-corporate brands like TATA, DABUR, HONDA, NESTLE, BAJAJ, BRITANNIA, PARLE , JINDAL and many more. Besides that, nearby G.B. Pant University, having a residential campus and 5500 students and 2500 faculty, supporting staff and their families. This gives ample reason to extract retail space treasure at the Metropolis Mall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine a gargantuan mall, so huge, so vast, and so fabulously varied in hue, light and design so Metropolis Mall is the perfect place to find all these characteristics in single space. Approximately 3,00,000 Sq. Ft. of pure shopping extended on three levels catering to women&#39;s wear, men&#39;s wear, a kid&#39;s zone , accessories, home furnishings and multi-brand products in huge anchor and retail shops. The Metropolis Mall with its hundreds of stores, restaurants, theaters, the Radisson Hotel with 120 rooms, Wave Cinemas will make other malls like small corner shops. It will become new age classic retail marvel with a high-tech research park for commercial R&amp;D and climate controlled biosphere for healthy recreation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The hypermarket in the Metropolis Mall has a very large retail facility which carries an enormous range of products under one roof. It is planned and constructed to satisfy a wide spectrum of routine shopping needs in one trip. The Entertainment Zone of this mall is built with multiplex which is all set to screen Bollywood &amp; Hollywood&#39;s recent offerings. Then, there is ample and large space for food delight. Food court that offers Indian, Mughlai, Chinese and Continental cuisine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Other salient feature of this mall is like a parking space for 900 cars, a very modern power back-up system that makes sure all vital electric feeds operating 24x7, 365.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_metropolis_1439788285.png', 'metropolis-pic1_1439788285.jpg', NULL, NULL, '1000000', '0', '2015-08-17 10:41:25', '2015-09-09 09:45:55', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '0000-00-00'),
(61, NULL, 'Hyphen Grand', 49, 'Welcome to Hyphen Grand, Haridwar', NULL, 'Haridwar', '0', '0', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>One of the finest hotels located in industrial hub of SIDCUL Haridwar, offers all services and facilities of a luxurious hotel at an extremely reasonable tariff. The hotel has been designed for modern-day business travelers and offers you all amenities that make your stay stress free and business trip successful.</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.hyphenhotels.com/" target="_blank"><img alt="Hyphen Grand Haridwar" src="/images/myphenharidwar.png" /></a></div>\r\n', 'logo-hyphen-hyphen_1439792712.png', 'hyphen-haridwar-pic1_1439792712.jpg', NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '2015-08-17 11:55:12', '2015-09-10 10:44:20', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 3, '0000-00-00'),
(62, NULL, 'Country Inn & Suites', 43, 'Country Inn & Suites', NULL, 'Meerut', '0', '0', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p><br />\r\nCountry Inn &amp; Suites by Carlson is located on Meerut Hapur Bypass in the commercial hub of Meerut City, adjacent to local attractions, Shopprix Mall, the historic church at Sardhana, the Shapir Mausoleum and Gandhi Bagh.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo_1439794273.gif', 'countryinn-pic1_1439794273.jpg', NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '2015-08-17 12:21:13', '2015-09-10 10:46:49', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 3, '0000-00-00'),
(63, '', 'Hyphen Premier', 43, 'Welcome to Hyphen Premier, Meerut', NULL, 'Meerut', '0', '0', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>The hotel located on Hapur Bypass is the perfect place to abode for a business trip or a leisure stay which is available at a very decent rate in Meerut city. All guest rooms are sleek, stylish and spacious with hi speed internet connectivity. Each room is provided with contemporary amenities and has been designed masterfully to accommodate all your needs.</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.hyphenhotels.com/" target="_blank"><img alt="Hyphen Premier Meerut" src="/images/hyphen-meerut.png" /></a></div>\r\n', 'logo-hyphen_1439795953.png', 'hpm-img1_1439795953.jpg', NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '2015-08-17 12:49:13', '2015-09-26 13:43:08', 1, 0, 0, 'http://www.hyphenhotels.com/', '', 3, '0000-00-00'),
(64, NULL, 'Radisson Blu', 45, 'Welcome to Radisson Blu, Rudrapur', NULL, 'Rudrapur', '0', '0', '<div class="over_col1">\r\n<p>The hotel located along NH-87 next to the business hub SIDCUL, is a perfect home base for experiencing Uttrakhand&#39;s industrial hub. Easily accessible attractions include Nanakmata, Ghullar Bhuj Dam, Jim Corbett National Park and Nainital-Bhimtal hill stations</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'logo-radisson_1439797183.png', 'radisson-rudrapur-pic1_1439797183.jpg', NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '2015-08-17 13:09:43', '2015-09-10 10:45:45', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 3, '0000-00-00'),
