(51, 58, '<div class="content_specifications">\r\n<div class="maintitle">Specifications</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Shopprix Mall comprises of 2 basements + LG + G+3 floors.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="spset1">\r\n<div class="spec_thumb"><img alt="Bedroom" border="0" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/spec_bedroom.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_text">\r\n<div class="spec_title">Lower Ground Floor</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_bull">A huge hyper market of approximately 75,000 sq.ft catering to all the daily needs of a household be it groceries, apparels, footwear, kitchenwares, house furnishings, and other so many national and international products.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_line">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_thumb"><img alt="Master Bedroom" border="0" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/spec_mbedroom.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_text">\r\n<div class="spec_title">Upper Ground Floor, First Floor and Second Floor</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_bull">Approx 2,50,000 sq.ft of pure shopping extended on three levels catering to women&#39;s wear, men&#39;s&#39; wear, footwears, kids zone, accessories, home furnishings and multi brand products in our huge anchors and retail shops. Products ranging from luxury goods to necessities, meeting all types of demands and tastes.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_bull">A unique concept of &quot;haat&quot; on second floor as a niche market for local retailers and traders for business opportunities in the mall and still part of this huge retail venture having an area of approx 18,000 sq.ft. An entertainment area on third floor dedicated to the kids with gaming zones and other sporting arcades having an area of approx. 31,000 sq.ft.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_bull">And last but not the least a huge food court on third floor with different counters, first of its kind in Uttar Pradesh and fine dining restaurants catering to all the tastes be it north &amp; south Indian, Chinese or continental all under one roof for everyday feast having an area of approx. 10,000 sq.ft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_line">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_thumb"><img alt="Bedroom" border="0" src="http://supertechlimited.com/images/spec_bedroom.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_text">\r\n<div class="spec_title">Third Floor, Fourth Floor and Fifth floor</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_bull">03 screens Wave Multiplex would be giving a never before experience to the customers.</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="spec_bull">A star grade hotel spanning over 1,20,000 sq.ft. As part of the mall on third, fourth and fifth floors with approx 85 rooms, with all amenities like luxurious rooms, excellent lobby, swimming pool, gymnasium, club house, banquet hall, etc. The entrance lobby aesthetically designed on the ground floor.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', ''),
